#. [hides], id=lurk
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/macros/abilities.cfg:9
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/macros/abilities.cfg:11
msgid "lurk"
msgstr "acechar"

#. [hides], id=lurk
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/macros/abilities.cfg:10
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/macros/abilities.cfg:12
msgid "female^lurk"
msgstr "acechar"

#. [hides], id=lurk
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/macros/abilities.cfg:13
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/macros/abilities.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Lurk:\n"
"This unit can hide in swamps, and remain undetected by its enemies.\n"
"\n"
"Enemy units cannot see this unit while it is in swamps, except if they have "
"units next to it. Any enemy unit that first discovers this unit immediately "
"loses all its remaining movement."
msgstr ""
"Acechar:\n"
"Esta unidad puede ocultarse en pantanos y pasar desapercibida para sus "
"enemigos.\n"
"\n"
"Las unidades enemigas no pueden ver a esta unidad mientras esté en un "
"pantano, a menos que tengan unidades adyacentes a ella. Cualquier unidad "
"enemiga que descubra a esta unidad por primera vez pierde de inmediato todo "
"su movimiento restante."

#. SPECIAL_NOTES
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/macros/special-notes.cfg:3
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"Special Notes:"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\n"
"Notas especiales:"

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_LURK
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/macros/special-notes.cfg:8
msgid ""
" In swampland, this unit's lurk skill renders it invisible to enemies unless "
"it is immediately adjacent or has revealed itself by attacking."
msgstr ""
" En terreno pantanoso, la habilidad de acecho de esta unidad la hace "
"invisible para los enemigos, a menos que estén directamente adyacentes a "
"ella o se haya revelado al atacar."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Auspex, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/unit-cfgs/Auspex.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Auspex"
msgstr "Auspex Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Auspex, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/unit-cfgs/Auspex.cfg:21
msgid ""
"One of the great mysteries of the Saurian tribes is their study of the "
"stars. While much of the Saurian culture is primative all Saurian magic "
"users are thoroughly schooled in the astrology and astronomy of the world, "
"and are immensely skilled in using the stars, moons, and planets as "
"divinitory tools and a source of power."
msgstr ""
"Uno de los grandes misterios de las tribus saurias es su estudio de las "
"estrellas. Aunque gran parte de la cultura sauria es primitiva, todos los "
"practicantes de magia saurios reciben una formación exhaustiva en astrología "
"y astronomía del mundo, y poseen una enorme habilidad para usar las "
"estrellas, lunas y planetas como herramientas adivinatorias y fuentes de "
"poder."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Haruspex, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/unit-cfgs/Haruspex.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Haruspex"
msgstr "Harúspice Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Haruspex, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/unit-cfgs/Haruspex.cfg:21
msgid ""
"While the appearance of the Haruspex is perhaps one of the least fearsome of "
"Saurians to appear on the battlefield, their deep understanding of "
"predictive magics is not to be underestimated. Gazing ever skyword and "
"whispering to the allies that invariably cluster near, the Haruspex's effect "
"on a battle can be both dramatic and immediate. While all of the Saurian "
"magic users are relied upon for their prophetic readings, the Haruspex "
"refine and focus upon that skill. It is said among the tribes that a "
"Haruspex cannot encounter death without having predicted it."
msgstr ""
"Aunque la apariencia del Harúspice es quizás la menos temible de los saurios "
"que aparecen en el campo de batalla, su profundo conocimiento de la magia "
"profética no debe subestimarse. Mirando siempre hacia el cielo y susurrando "
"a los aliados que invariablemente se agrupan a su alrededor, el efecto del "
"Harúspice en una batalla puede ser tanto dramático como inmediato. Si bien "
"todos los practicantes de magia saurios son apreciados por sus lecturas "
"proféticas, el Harúspice refina y se centra en esa habilidad. Entre las "
"tribus se dice que un Harúspice no puede encontrar la muerte sin haberla "
"predicho."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Hunter, race=lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Hunter, race=lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/unit-cfgs/Hunter.cfg:4
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S1-Hunter.cfg:5
msgid "Saurian Hunter"
msgstr "Cazador Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Hunter, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/unit-cfgs/Hunter.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Saurian warriors derive their tactics from their hunting methods, and even "
"the greatest of Saurian warriors is still responsible for bringing back food "
"for the tribe."
msgstr ""
"Los guerreros saurios derivan sus tácticas de sus métodos de caza, y hasta "
"el más grande de los guerreros saurios sigue siendo responsable de traer "
"alimento para la tribu."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Observer, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/unit-cfgs/Observer.cfg:4
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/unit-cfgs/Vigilant.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Observer"
msgstr "Observador Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Observer, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/unit-cfgs/Observer.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Far weaker in a fair fight than even the most frail of elves or humans, "
"outsiders encountering Observers easily mistake them for dark and vengful "
"spirits as they strike and then melt away. Frequently, by the time an "
"Observer leads their hunting party to it's prey the members of the hunting "
"party have ample ready targets."
msgstr ""
"Mucho más débiles en combate directo que incluso los más frágiles elfos o "
"humanos, quienes se topan con los Observadores los confunden fácilmente con "
"espíritus oscuros y vengativos que golpean y luego se desvanecen. Con "
"frecuencia, para cuando un Observador lleva a su grupo de caza hasta su "
"presa, los miembros del grupo ya tienen abundantes objetivos al alcance."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=ranged
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/unit-cfgs/Observer.cfg:63
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/unit-cfgs/Vigilant.cfg:66
msgid "poison darts"
msgstr "dardos envenenados"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Observer, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/unit-cfgs/Vigilant.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Living in shadows and darkness, those Saurians who excell at stealth and "
"trechery become fearsome legends among the tribes and are the source of many "
"horrific stories among nearby communities of non-Saurians."
msgstr ""
"Viviendo entre sombras y oscuridad, los saurios que sobresalen en el sigilo "
"y la traición se convierten en leyendas temibles entre las tribus y son el "
"origen de numerosas historias aterradoras entre las comunidades cercanas de "
"no-saurios."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Watcher, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/unit-cfgs/Watcher.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Watcher"
msgstr "Vigilante Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Watcher, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Darker_Dreams/unit-cfgs/Watcher.cfg:20
msgid ""
"The best weapon the Saurians posess is stealth, their ability to slide past "
"their enemies guards and find ways to assault the weakest links of their "
"foes. Some saurians choose to cultivate their gifts of stealth and surprise "
"which flow from their natural litheness rather than work towards more "
"powerful blows. Rarely seen, watchers are the forward scouts of Saurian "
"hunting bands. Among a race which values those traits inherant to a scout, "
"the abilities of Watchers would terrify outsiders if they were better known. "
"These Saurians travel lightly, wearing no armor or equipment aside from a "
"knife and a dart-blower. Because they carry no gear, even rations, their "
"life relies on constantly leading their party on successful hunts or "
"scavanging."
msgstr ""
"La mejor arma que poseen los saurios es el sigilo: su capacidad para "
"escabullirse ante las guardias enemigas y encontrar la manera de atacar los "
"eslabones más débiles de sus rivales. Algunos saurios eligen cultivar sus "
"dones de sigilo y sorpresa, que emanan de su agilidad natural, en lugar de "
"aspirar a golpes más poderosos. Raramente vistos, los Vigilantes son los "
"exploradores de vanguardia de las bandas de caza saurias. Entre una raza que "
"valora los rasgos propios de un explorador, las capacidades de los "
"Vigilantes aterrorizarían a los forasteros si fueran más conocidas. Estos "
"saurios viajan ligeros, sin armadura ni equipo salvo un cuchillo y una "
"cerbatana. Como no cargan con provisiones, ni siquiera raciones, su vida "
"depende de liderar constantemente a su grupo en cacerías exitosas o en la "
"carroña."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Spearmaster, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Evelangos/Spearmaster.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Spearmaster"
msgstr "Maestro de Lanza Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Spearmaster, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Evelangos/Spearmaster.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Saurian warriors are generally weaker in frame than their elven, or human "
"counterparts. This is of course a relative term, and they can still become "
"considerably powerful, whilst losing none of their natural mobility. This is "
"an elite rank of feminine Saurians who have gone throughout a load of "
"trouble with the ideals of gender to use their strength and have even come "
"to use dance as a weapon, but as all know, the dance of any serpent is "
"almost assuredly fatal if one gives in."
msgstr ""
"Los guerreros saurios son en general más débiles de complexión que sus "
"contrapartes elfas o humanas. Esto es, por supuesto, un término relativo, y "
"aun así pueden llegar a ser considerablemente poderosos sin perder nada de "
"su movilidad natural. Este es un rango de élite de saurias femeninas que han "
"superado grandes obstáculos relacionados con los ideales de género para "
"emplear su fuerza, e incluso han llegado a usar la danza como arma; pero "
"como todos saben, la danza de cualquier serpiente es casi con certeza fatal "
"para quien cede ante ella."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=ranged
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/Evelangos/Spearmaster.cfg:73
msgid "Disc"
msgstr "Disco"

#. [unit_type], id=Z Shaman2, race=zaxal2
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/a1_Z_Shaman.cfg:5
msgid "Zaxali Shaman"
msgstr "Chamán Zaxali"

#. [unit_type], id=Z Shaman2, race=zaxal2
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/a1_Z_Shaman.cfg:20
msgid ""
"The few Zaxali that have power over water are trained from a young age as "
"Shamans."
msgstr ""
"Los pocos Zaxali que tienen poder sobre el agua son entrenados desde jóvenes "
"como Chamanes."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=ranged
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/a1_Z_Shaman.cfg:48
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/a2_Z_Witch_Doctor.cfg:49
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/a3_Z_Master_Shaman.cfg:50
msgid "swamp strike"
msgstr "golpe pantanoso"

#. [unit_type], id=Z Witch Doctor2, race=zaxal2, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/a2_Z_Witch_Doctor.cfg:5
msgid "Zaxali Witch Doctor"
msgstr "Médico Brujo Zaxali"

#. [unit_type], id=Z Witch Doctor2, race=zaxal2, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/a2_Z_Witch_Doctor.cfg:21
msgid ""
"More skilled Shamans become Witch Doctors, who take care of the sick and "
"dead."
msgstr ""
"Los Chamanes más hábiles se convierten en Médicos Brujos, que se ocupan de "
"los enfermos y los muertos."

#. [unit_type], id=Z Master Shaman2, race=zaxal2, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/a3_Z_Master_Shaman.cfg:5
msgid "Zaxali Master Shaman"
msgstr "Gran Chamán Zaxali"

#. [unit_type], id=Z Master Shaman2, race=zaxal2, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/a3_Z_Master_Shaman.cfg:22
msgid ""
"Few Master Shamans are to be found on Kraman, most of them never made the "
"crossing from Rashi."
msgstr ""
"Pocos Grandes Chamanes se encuentran en Kraman; la mayoría nunca realizó la "
"travesía desde Rashi."

#. [unit_type], id=Z Feldrix2, race=zaxal2, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/b1_Z_Feldrix.cfg:5
msgid "Zaxali Feldrix"
msgstr "Feldrix Zaxali"

#. [unit_type], id=Z Feldrix2, race=zaxal2, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/b1_Z_Feldrix.cfg:21
msgid ""
"The fighting caste of the Zaxali society. The Feldrix are those completely "
"unnattuned to magic, as the weapons they carry, either brought over from "
"Rashi or gained by way of pillage or trade from the Zaxali's neighbors, are "
"rare, and so can only to be given to those who truly have no other calling."
msgstr ""
"La casta guerrera de la sociedad Zaxali. Los Feldrix son aquellos "
"completamente desconectados de la magia; las armas que portan, traídas de "
"Rashi o conseguidas mediante el pillaje o el comercio con los vecinos de los "
"Zaxali, son escasas y por ello solo pueden darse a quienes verdaderamente no "
"tienen otro destino."

#. [unit_type], id=Z Warrior2, race=zaxal2, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/b2_Z_Warrior.cfg:5
msgid "Zaxali Warrior"
msgstr "Guerrero Zaxali"

#. [unit_type], id=Z Warrior2, race=zaxal2, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/b2_Z_Warrior.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Though there is no real title difference between the Feldrix and the "
"warriors, the warriors have had more chance to lift weapons and armour from "
"fallen opponents, and to return victorious from the battlefield."
msgstr ""
"Aunque no hay una diferencia real de título entre los Feldrix y los "
"guerreros, estos últimos han tenido más oportunidades de tomar armas y "
"armaduras de enemigos caídos y de regresar victoriosamente del campo de "
"batalla."

#. [unit_type], id=Z Eternal2, race=zaxal2, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/b3_Z_Eternal.cfg:5
msgid "Zaxali Eternal"
msgstr "Eterno Zaxali"

#. [unit_type], id=Z Eternal2, race=zaxal2, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/b3_Z_Eternal.cfg:22
msgid ""
"The Eternals are rarer still than the Master Shamans on Kraman, they are "
"truly masters of their art and can hold their own against Kuandigin "
"Guardians."
msgstr ""
"Los Eternos son aún más raros que los Grandes Chamanes en Kraman; son "
"verdaderos maestros de su arte y pueden mantenerse en pie frente a los "
"Guardianes Kuandigin."

#. [unit_type], id=Z Hunter2, race=zaxal2
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/c1_Z_Hunter.cfg:5
msgid "Zaxali Hunter"
msgstr "Cazador Zaxali"

#. [unit_type], id=Z Hunter2, race=zaxal2
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/c1_Z_Hunter.cfg:20
msgid ""
"The bulk of the Zaxali society, these lizards gather food and scout out the "
"swamps."
msgstr ""
"La mayoría de la sociedad Zaxali, estos lagartos recolectan alimento y "
"exploran los pantanos."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=ranged
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/c1_Z_Hunter.cfg:49
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/c2_Z_Stalker.cfg:50
msgid "blowpipe"
msgstr "cerbatana"

#. [unit_type], id=Z Stalker2, race=zaxal2
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/c2_Z_Stalker.cfg:5
msgid "Zaxali Stalker"
msgstr "Acechador Zaxali"

#. [unit_type], id=Z Stalker2, race=zaxal2
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/c2_Z_Stalker.cfg:21
msgid ""
"More skilled hunters are also delegated to the task of shadowing outsiders "
"that enter the swamps."
msgstr ""
"Los cazadores más hábiles también son designados para la tarea de seguir a "
"los forasteros que se adentran en los pantanos."

#. [unit_type], id=Z Reefthrower2, race=zaxal2
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/e1_Z_Reefthrower.cfg:5
msgid "Zaxali Reefthrower"
msgstr "Lanzarrecifes Zaxali"

#. [unit_type], id=Z Reefthrower2, race=zaxal2
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/e1_Z_Reefthrower.cfg:21
msgid ""
"The Reefthrowers are not true Zaxali, but are welcomed intot he society. "
"They, like the Zaxali, came from Rashi."
msgstr ""
"Los Lanzarrecifes no son Zaxali de pura cepa, pero son bienvenidos en la "
"sociedad. Ellos, al igual que los Zaxali, vinieron de Rashi."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=ranged
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/The_Dark_Master/saurians-zaxalis/e1_Z_Reefthrower.cfg:35
msgid "boulder"
msgstr "peñasco"

#. [unit_type], id=IQ Saurian Blind Seer, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/inkys_quest/IQ_Blind_Seer.cfg:6
msgid "Saurian Blind Seer"
msgstr "Vidente Ciego Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=IQ Saurian Blind Seer, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/inkys_quest/IQ_Blind_Seer.cfg:27
msgid ""
"This Saurian shaman has lost his eyesight, but this traumatic experience has "
"given him an insight normally unheard in his kin. Both his healing and "
"destructive magic have improved as a result of this."
msgstr ""
"Este chamán saurio ha perdido la vista, pero esta experiencia traumática le "
"ha otorgado una perspicacia inusual entre los de su especie. Tanto su magia "
"curativa como la destructiva han mejorado como resultado de ello."

#. [unit_type], id=IQ Saurian Concoctionist, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/inkys_quest/IQ_Saurian_Concoctionist.cfg:7
msgid "Saurian Concoctionist"
msgstr "Preparador Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=IQ Saurian Concoctionist, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/inkys_quest/IQ_Saurian_Concoctionist.cfg:35
msgid ""
"This saurian shaman always carries a large cauldron where he cooks various "
"magical concoctions, such as healing potions, deadly posions or blinding "
"mist."
msgstr ""
"Este chamán saurio siempre carga con un gran caldero en el que prepara "
"diversas pociones mágicas, como brebajes curativos, venenos mortales o "
"niebla cegadora."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/inkys_quest/IQ_Saurian_Concoctionist.cfg:73
msgid "poisonous touch"
msgstr "toque venenoso"

#. [attack], type=impact, range=ranged
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/inkys_quest/IQ_Saurian_Concoctionist.cfg:97
msgid "poisonous vapors"
msgstr "vapores venenosos"

#. [unit_type], id=IQ Saurian Thunderer, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/inkys_quest/IQ_Saurian_Thunderer.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Thunderer"
msgstr "Atronador Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=IQ Saurian Thunderer, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/inkys_quest/IQ_Saurian_Thunderer.cfg:19
msgid ""
"This Saurian has stolen a dwarvish thunderstick and learned how to use it. "
"However, he lacks the skill of trained dwarvish thunderers."
msgstr ""
"Este saurio ha robado una atronadora enana y ha aprendido a usarla. Sin "
"embargo, le falta la destreza de los atronadores enanos entrenados."

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Armorer, race=exi_lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Armorer, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Armor_Armorer.cfg:4
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S2-Armorer.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Armorer"
msgstr "Armero Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Armorer, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Armor_Armorer.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Saurian recruits are aspiring to become skilled in the use of the spear. "
"Despite their lethargic cold blooded heritage, and their relative frailty, "
"recruits are highly valued as they can navigate through rough terrain and "
"around opponents. The best recruits go on to become Saurian Guards."
msgstr ""
"Los reclutas saurios aspiran a perfeccionarse en el uso de la lanza. A pesar "
"de su lánguida herencia de sangre fría y su relativa fragilidad, los "
"reclutas son muy valorados por su capacidad para moverse por terreno difícil "
"y sortear a los enemigos. Los mejores reclutas llegan a convertirse en "
"Guardias Saurios."

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Guardian, race=exi_lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Armor_Guard.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Guardian"
msgstr "Guardián Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Guardian, race=exi_lizard, gender=male
#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Protector, race=exi_lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Armor_Guard.cfg:20
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Armor_Protector.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Saurian guards are clad in heavy armor and use an spear that cuts aswell as "
"it pierces. They are fiercely loyal to their tribe and fight alongside their "
"chieftain at every opportunity."
msgstr ""
"Los guardias saurios van enfundados en armadura pesada y usan una lanza que "
"tanto corta como atraviesa. Son ferozmente leales a su tribu y combaten "
"junto a su jefe en toda ocasión."

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Protector, race=exi_lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Armor_Protector.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Protector"
msgstr "Protector Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Necrolyte, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Dark_Necrolyte.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Necrolyte"
msgstr "Necrólito Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Necrolyte, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Dark_Necrolyte.cfg:19
msgid ""
"The dark ritualist lives at the fringes of saurian society, despite being "
"seen as an heretic and living as an outcast for dabbling in truely black "
"magic, his service becomes necessary for when the rite of passage into the "
"otherworld has to occur for an recently dead saurian."
msgstr ""
"El ritualista oscuro vive en los márgenes de la sociedad sauria; aunque es "
"visto como un hereje y vive como un paria por adentrarse en la magia "
"verdaderamente negra, sus servicios se vuelven necesarios cuando debe "
"realizarse el rito de paso al más allá para un saurio recién fallecido."

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Ritualist, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Dark_Ritualist.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Ritualist"
msgstr "Ritualista Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Ritualist, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Dark_Ritualist.cfg:18
msgid ""
"The dark ritualist lives at the fringes of saurian society,despite being "
"seen as an heretic and living as an outcast for dabbling in truely black "
"magic, his service becomes necessary for when the rite of passage into the "
"otherworld has to occur for an recently dead saurian."
msgstr ""
"El ritualista oscuro vive en los márgenes de la sociedad sauria; aunque es "
"visto como un hereje y vive como un paria por adentrarse en la magia "
"verdaderamente negra, sus servicios se vuelven necesarios cuando debe "
"realizarse el rito de paso al más allá para un saurio recién fallecido."

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Beastmaster, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Drakeling_Beastmaster.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Beastmaster"
msgstr "Domador de Bestias Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Beastmaster, race=exi_lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Tamer, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Drakeling_Beastmaster.cfg:19
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Drakeling_Tamer.cfg:18
msgid ""
"The Saurian tamers are an vicious bunch. They get themselves an drake egg, "
"often through less desireable methods such as theft, and watch over it until "
"an drakeling hatches. Then they enslave the young drake and goad it into "
"battle as if its an war-dog."
msgstr ""
"Los domadores saurios son una pandilla despiadada. Se consiguen un huevo de "
"draco, a menudo por métodos poco deseables como el robo, y lo vigilan hasta "
"que eclosiona una cría de draco. Luego esclavizan al joven draco y lo "
"incitan a la batalla como si fuera un perro de guerra."

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Tamer, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Drakeling_Tamer.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Tamer"
msgstr "Domador Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Hill Saurian, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Hammer_Hill.cfg:4
msgid "Hill Saurian"
msgstr "Saurio de las Colinas"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Hill Saurian, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Hammer_Hill.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Hill Saurian are named such for spending their time searching and extracting "
"the ore for they are the tribe's blacksmiths. They forge themselves an "
"chainmail armor to wear with pride, at times of war they like to bash heads "
"of opponents with the heavy hammer they work with."
msgstr ""
"Los Saurios de las Colinas reciben ese nombre por pasar su tiempo buscando y "
"extrayendo mineral, pues son los herreros de la tribu. Se forjan una "
"armadura de cota de malla que lucen con orgullo; en tiempos de guerra les "
"gusta aplastar cabezas enemigas con el pesado martillo con el que trabajan."

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Mountain Saurian, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Hammer_Mountain.cfg:4
msgid "Mountain Saurian"
msgstr "Saurio de las Montañas"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Mountain Saurian, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Hammer_Mountain.cfg:19
msgid ""
"The more experienced of the saurian smiths have gained the ability to travel "
"through mountain and hills with ease in their search for precious rare ore "
"to work with."
msgstr ""
"Los herreros saurios más experimentados han adquirido la capacidad de "
"recorrer montañas y colinas con facilidad en su búsqueda de mineral raro y "
"precioso con el que trabajar."

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Trainee, race=exi_lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Knife_Trainee.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Trainee"
msgstr "Aprendiz Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Trainee, race=exi_lizard, gender=male
#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Knifethrower Thief, race=thief-lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Knifethrower, race=thief-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Knife_Trainee.cfg:19
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S1-Knifethrower-thief.cfg:17
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S1-Knifethrower.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Some saurians take up the path of stealth, those practice fighting with "
"daggers and throwing knives."
msgstr ""
"Algunos saurios emprenden el camino del sigilo; estos se ejercitan en el "
"combate con dagas y cuchillos arrojadizos."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=short
#. [attack], type=blade, range=ranged
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Knife_Trainee.cfg:45
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S1-Milita.cfg:46
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S2-Soldier.cfg:47
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S3-Knight.cfg:48
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S1-Knifethrower-thief.cfg:44
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S1-Knifethrower.cfg:44
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S2-Seeker-thief.cfg:49
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S2-Seeker.cfg:49
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S3-Slayer-thief.cfg:51
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S3-Slayer.cfg:51
msgid "throwing knife"
msgstr "cuchillo arrojadizo"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Lizard Master, race=exi_lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Lizard_Master.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Chieftain"
msgstr "Jefe Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Lizard Master, race=exi_lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Lizard_Master.cfg:21
msgid ""
"The larger, beastly reptiles dwelling in the swamp are tamed and then got to "
"be ridden by the saurian chieftains, who lead their tribe into battle "
"wearing the best armor."
msgstr ""
"Los reptiles más grandes y bestiales que habitan en el pantano son domados y "
"luego montados por los jefes saurios, quienes conducen a su tribu a la "
"batalla luciendo la mejor armadura."

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Lizard Rider, race=exi_lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Lizard_Rider.cfg:4
msgid "Lizard Rider"
msgstr "Jinete de Lagarto"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Lizard Rider, race=exi_lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Lizard_Rider.cfg:20
msgid ""
"The larger, beastly reptiles dwelling in the swamp are tamed and then get "
"ridden by Saurian warriors, who goad them on to find prey suitable for "
"dinner."
msgstr ""
"Los reptiles más grandes y bestiales que habitan en el pantano son domados y "
"luego montados por guerreros saurios, que los incitan a buscar presas "
"adecuadas para la cena."

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Despoiler, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Magic_Despoiler.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Despoiler"
msgstr "Devastador Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Despoiler, race=exi_lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Elementalist, race=exi_lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Profaner, race=exi_lizard
