#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Magic_Summoner.cfg:42
msgid "fire ball"
msgstr "bola de fuego"

#. [attack], type=cold, range=ranged
#. [attack], type=cold, range=short
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Magic_Elementalist.cfg:56
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Magic_Elementalist.cfg:69
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Magic_Summoner.cfg:55
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Magic_Summoner.cfg:68
msgid "ice ball"
msgstr "bola de hielo"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Profaner, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Magic_Profaner.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Profaner"
msgstr "Profanador Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Sorceror, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Magic_Sorceror.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Sorceror"
msgstr "Hechicero Saurio"

#. [attack], type=cold, range=short
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Magic_Sorceror.cfg:42
msgid "cold wave"
msgstr "ola de frío"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Summoner, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Magic_Summoner.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Summoner"
msgstr "Invocador Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Skald, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Skald.cfg:4
msgid "Skald"
msgstr "Skald"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Skald, race=exi_lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Exi Skald Frenzy, race=exi_lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Exi Skald Youth, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Skald.cfg:17
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Skald_Frenzy.cfg:17
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Skald_Youth.cfg:17
msgid ""
"The Skalds are an different, some would say flawed, breed of saurians which "
"can grow to monstrous sizes, and thus are considerably tougher, but move "
"slower. They are defined by their poisonous bite which they use as a last "
"resort, as their poison containers swell and bloat at continued use, "
"negatively effecting the mental health of the creature."
msgstr ""
"Los Skalds son una raza diferente, algunos dirían defectuosa, de saurios que "
"pueden crecer hasta tamaños monstruosos y son considerablemente más "
"resistentes, aunque se mueven más lentamente. Se distinguen por su mordedura "
"venenosa, que usan como último recurso, ya que sus glándulas de veneno se "
"hinchan y dilatan con el uso continuado, afectando negativamente la salud "
"mental de la criatura."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=melee
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Skald.cfg:35
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Skald_Frenzy.cfg:38
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Skald_Maniac.cfg:39
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Skald_Youth.cfg:35
msgid "poisonous bite"
msgstr "mordedura venenosa"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Skald Frenzy, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Skald_Frenzy.cfg:4
msgid "Skald Frenzy"
msgstr "Skald Frenético"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Skald Maniac, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Skald_Maniac.cfg:4
msgid "Skald Maniac"
msgstr "Skald Maníaco"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Skald Maniac, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Skald_Maniac.cfg:18
msgid ""
"The poison of the Skalds sometimes affects their mind in a nasty way. Those "
"skalds that have a high concentration of it are driven insane from the pain, "
"they are called maniacs by their kind because they enter battle with a "
"frenzy unmatched by any other, wrestling their opponent to the ground and "
"then ripping him to pieces with dagger and claw."
msgstr ""
"El veneno de los Skalds a veces afecta su mente de forma terrible. Aquellos "
"Skalds con una alta concentración de veneno enloquecen a causa del dolor; "
"sus congéneres los llaman maníacos porque entran en batalla con un frenesí "
"sin igual, derribando a su adversario al suelo para luego despedazarlo con "
"daga y garra."

