msgid "Saurian Duelist"
msgstr "Duelista Saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Duelist, race=exi_lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Exi Saurian Gladiator, race=exi_lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Sword_Duelist.cfg:18
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/images/units/unused/saurian-swamp/Sword_Gladiator.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Saurians are as a whole primitive savages, lacking both the technology and "
"the discipline to produce truly effective soldiers. Ocasionally however a "
"saurian is given equipment and training by more advanced races, often "
"captives taken from their tribe and groomed as contestants in blood sport or "
"as conscript soldiers. The combination of their superior agility with "
"advanced weaponry and combat technique makes them skilled and deadly "
"opponents; those that manage to escape their fate and rejoin their tribe are "
"inevitably destined to become great champions among their people."
msgstr ""
"Los saurios son en general salvajes primitivos, carentes tanto de la "
"tecnología como de la disciplina para producir soldados verdaderamente "
"eficaces. Sin embargo, en ocasiones un saurio recibe equipamiento y "
"entrenamiento de razas más avanzadas, a menudo como cautivo arrancado de su "
"tribu y preparado como contendiente en deportes de sangre o como soldado de "
"leva. La combinación de su agilidad superior con armamento avanzado y "
"técnica de combate los convierte en adversarios hábiles y letales; quienes "
"logran escapar a su destino y reunirse con su tribu están inevitablemente "
"destinados a convertirse en grandes campeones entre los suyos."

