#. [unit_type], id=Witch Doctor Hero, race=bitter-swamp-lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Witch Doctor, race=bitter-swamp-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-Ikta_Tosh.cfg:4
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Witch_Doctor.cfg:4
msgid "Witch Doctor"
msgstr "Médico brujo"

#. [unit_type], id=Witch Doctor Hero, race=bitter-swamp-lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Witch Doctor, race=bitter-swamp-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-Ikta_Tosh.cfg:19
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Witch_Doctor.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Despite their lethargic cold blooded heritage, and their relative frailty, "
"Witch doctors are nevertheless valued in the battlefield for the aid they "
"provide to wounded allies as well as feared for their ability to turn normal "
"swamp water to a dreaded acid. Every saurian tribe has at least one witch "
"doctor who is revered and protected."
msgstr ""
"A pesar de su herencia de sangre fría y su relativa fragilidad, los médicos "
"brujos son valorados en el campo de batalla por la ayuda que brindan a sus "
"aliados heridos y temidos por su capacidad de convertir el agua normal del "
"pantano en un ácido temible. Cada tribu sauria tiene al menos un médico "
"brujo que es reverenciado y protegido."

#. [attack], type=fire, range=melee
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-Ikta_Tosh.cfg:53
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Witch_Doctor.cfg:37
msgid "acid spray"
msgstr "rociada de ácido"

#. [unit_type], id=Swamp Alchemist Hero, race=bitter-swamp-lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Swamp Alchemist, race=bitter-swamp-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-Ikta_Tosh.cfg:113
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Swamp_Alchemist.cfg:4
msgid "Swamp Alchemist"
msgstr "Alquimista del pantano"

#. [unit_type], id=Swamp Alchemist Hero, race=bitter-swamp-lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Swamp Alchemist, race=bitter-swamp-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-Ikta_Tosh.cfg:128
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Swamp_Alchemist.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Some witch doctors are so in tune with their environment that after a while "
"they take a long journey into the swamps alone. No-one knows what they do "
"but when they return their mastery of the secret recipes hidden in the murky "
"waters is unparalleled. Many a warrior has seen his ally turn into melting "
"bones inside his armor from their powerful acid attacks."
msgstr ""
"Algunos médicos brujos están tan en sintonía con su entorno que después de "
"un tiempo emprenden un largo viaje solos hacia los pantanos. Nadie sabe qué "
"hacen, pero cuando regresan su dominio de las recetas secretas ocultas en "
"las aguas turbias es inigualable. Muchos guerreros han visto a su aliado "
"convertirse en huesos derretidos dentro de su armadura por sus poderosos "
"ataques de ácido."

#. [attack], type=fire, range=melee
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-Ikta_Tosh.cfg:162
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-Ikta_Tosh.cfg:295
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Swamp_Alchemist.cfg:37
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Swamp_Lord.cfg:40
msgid "acid shower"
msgstr "lluvia de ácido"

#. [attack], type=fire, range=ranged
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-Ikta_Tosh.cfg:174
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-Ikta_Tosh.cfg:307
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Swamp_Alchemist.cfg:49
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Swamp_Lord.cfg:52
msgid "acid bolt"
msgstr "proyectil de ácido"

#. [unit_type], id=Swamp Lord Hero, race=bitter-swamp-lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Swamp Lord, race=bitter-swamp-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-Ikta_Tosh.cfg:245
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Swamp_Lord.cfg:4
msgid "Swamp Lord"
msgstr "Señor del pantano"

#. [unit_type], id=Swamp Lord Hero, race=bitter-swamp-lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Swamp Lord, race=bitter-swamp-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-Ikta_Tosh.cfg:261
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Swamp_Lord.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Swamp Lords are masters of the natural home of the saurians. Their knowledge "
"of the arcane energies and rare herbs hidden within is unparalelled. When a "
"swamp lord decides to move, the swamp moves with him."
msgstr ""
"Los señores del pantano son maestros del hogar natural de los saurios. Su "
"conocimiento de las energías arcanas y las hierbas raras ocultas en él es "
"inigualable. Cuando un señor del pantano decide moverse, el pantano se mueve "
"con él."

#. [unit_type], id=Bloodborn, race=bitter-swamp-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-S'Saskin.cfg:4
msgid "Bloodborn"
msgstr "Nacido de la sangre"

#. [unit_type], id=Bloodborn, race=bitter-swamp-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-S'Saskin.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Bloodborns are considered by the saurians as the sign of a natural leader. "
"The name comes from the way they come out of their womb. They eat though it, "
"killing their mother in the process. Considering that saurians are born in "
"eggs, this is a big difference.\n"
"Bloodborns are very violent and demanding but also respected and feared by "
"the rest of the tribe. Their bite is always poisonous but they prefer to "
"enter battle with the nastiest weapon they can find."
msgstr ""
"Los nacidos de la sangre son considerados por los saurios como la señal de "
"un líder natural. El nombre proviene de la forma en que salen del vientre. "
"Se comen el camino a través de él, matando a su madre en el proceso. "
"Considerando que los saurios nacen de huevos, esto es una gran diferencia.\n"
"Los nacidos de la sangre son muy violentos y exigentes, pero también son "
"respetados y temidos por el resto de la tribu. Su mordida siempre es "
"venenosa, pero prefieren entrar en batalla con el arma más desagradable que "
"puedan encontrar."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-S'Saskin.cfg:26
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-S'Saskin.cfg:122
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-S'Saskin.cfg:219
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S2-Warrior(Refumee).cfg:45
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S3-Champion(Refumee).cfg:46
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S2-Pikemen.cfg:45
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S3-Heavy-Pikemen.cfg:46
msgid "halberd slash"
msgstr "corte de alabarda"

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=melee
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-S'Saskin.cfg:35
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-S'Saskin.cfg:131
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-S'Saskin.cfg:228
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S1-Ghoul.cfg:40
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S2-Runner.cfg:43
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S3-Sprinter.cfg:45
msgid "poison bite"
msgstr "mordida venenosa"

#. [unit_type], id=Bloodborns Chieftain, race=bitter-swamp-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-S'Saskin.cfg:81
msgid "Bloodborns Chieftain"
msgstr "Jefe de los nacidos de la sangre"

#. [unit_type], id=Bloodborns Chieftain, race=bitter-swamp-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-S'Saskin.cfg:94
msgid ""
"When bloodborns have proved themselves in battle the tribe will give them "
"one last test; They must hunt down the old chief and kill him bare-handed as "
"a sign of prowess. If they make it out alive, they become the tribe's new "
"chief. Tribes led by bloodborn are always the most powerful and influential."
msgstr ""
"Cuando los nacidos de la sangre se han probado en batalla, la tribu les da "
"una última prueba: deben cazar al viejo jefe y matarlo con sus propias manos "
"como muestra de destreza. Si salen vivos, se convierten en el nuevo jefe de "
"la tribu. Las tribus lideradas por nacidos de la sangre siempre son las más "
"poderosas e influyentes."

#. [unit_type], id=Bloodchosen, race=bitter-swamp-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-S'Saskin.cfg:177
msgid "The Blood Chosen"
msgstr "El Elegido de la Sangre"

#. [unit_type], id=Bloodchosen, race=bitter-swamp-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/bitter-swamp-saurians/Hero-S'Saskin.cfg:191
msgid ""
"When a bloodborn chief manages to subdue many other saurian tribes, the "
"saurians proclaim him The Blood Chosen. He has proven himself the undisputed "
"leader of the saurian race, and under his rule they will prosper."
msgstr ""
"Cuando un jefe nacido de la sangre logra someter a muchas otras tribus "
"saurias, los saurios lo proclaman El Elegido de la Sangre. Ha demostrado ser "
"el líder indiscutible de la raza sauria, y bajo su mando prosperarán."

#. [unit_type], id=Young Saurian, race=black-marshes-saurians
#. [unit_type], id=Ref Young Saurian, race=lizard, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Deep Young Saurian, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S0-Young.cfg:4
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S0-Young.cfg:4
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S0-Young.cfg:4
msgid "Young Saurian"
msgstr "Saurio joven"

#. [unit_type], id=Young Saurian, race=black-marshes-saurians
#. [unit_type], id=Ref Young Saurian, race=lizard, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Ref Young Saurian Zombie, race=undead-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S0-Young.cfg:17
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S0-Young.cfg:24
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S0-Zombie-Spear.cfg:19
msgid "Young Saurians work for Drakes, mostly as miners."
msgstr ""
"Los saurios jóvenes trabajan para los dracos, principalmente como mineros."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Blacksmith, race=black-marshes-saurians
#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Blacksmith, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S1-Blacksmith.cfg:4
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S1-Blacksmith.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Blacksmith"
msgstr "Herrero saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Blacksmith, race=black-marshes-saurians
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S1-Blacksmith.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Some young lizards prefer to keep working for the community, instead of "
"becoming soldiers. Blacksmith is one of them."
msgstr ""
"Algunos lagartos jóvenes prefieren seguir trabajando para la comunidad en "
"lugar de convertirse en soldados. El herrero es uno de ellos."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Fighter, race=black-marshes-saurians
#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Fighter, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S1-Fighter.cfg:4
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S1-Fighter.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Fighter"
msgstr "Luchador saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Fighter, race=black-marshes-saurians
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S1-Fighter.cfg:17
msgid "Saurian Fighter is a soldier-type in the race."
msgstr "El luchador saurio es un tipo de soldado dentro de la raza."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=ranged
