#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Craftsman, race=black-marshes-saurians
#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Craftsman, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S2-Craftsman.cfg:4
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S2-Craftsman.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Craftsman"
msgstr "Artesano saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Craftsman, race=black-marshes-saurians
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S2-Craftsman.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Saurian Blacksmiths become Craftsmen who create and develop the weapons for "
"Saurians. "
msgstr ""
"Los herreros saurios se convierten en artesanos que crean y desarrollan las "
"armas para los saurios."

#. [advancement], id=amla_thunderstick
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S2-Craftsman.cfg:30
msgid "new powder formula (+2 damage to thunderstick, no heal full)"
msgstr ""
"nueva fórmula de pólvora (+2 de daño a la vara de trueno, sin sanación "
"completa)"

#. [advancement], id=ato_amla_marksman
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S2-Craftsman.cfg:44
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S3-Artist.cfg:28
msgid "marksman (marksman attack is given to the ranged attack)"
msgstr "tirador (el ataque de tirador se otorga al ataque a distancia)"

#. [advancement], id=ato_amla_firststrike
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S2-Craftsman.cfg:59
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S3-Artist.cfg:43
msgid "first strike (firststrike is given to the ranged attack)"
msgstr "primer golpe (el primer golpe se otorga al ataque a distancia)"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Guard, race=black-marshes-saurians
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S2-Guard.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Guard"
msgstr "Guardia saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Guard, race=black-marshes-saurians
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S2-Guard.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Saurian guards are experts in the use of the spear. They are fiercely loyal "
"to their commander and fight alongside him at every opportunity. Their "
"combat style is based upon weakening an enemy with a poisoned throwing "
"spear, then closing and using their regular spears to finish the battle."
msgstr ""
"Los guardias saurios son expertos en el uso de la lanza. Son ferozmente "
"leales a su comandante y luchan a su lado en cada oportunidad. Su estilo de "
"combate se basa en debilitar a un enemigo con una lanza arrojadiza "
"envenenada, luego acercarse y usar sus lanzas normales para terminar la "
"batalla."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=melee
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S2-Guard.cfg:32
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S3-Champion.cfg:34
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S2-Peltast.cfg:35
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S3-Heavy-Peltast.cfg:36
msgid "longspear"
msgstr "lanza larga"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Sage, race=black-marshes-saurians
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S2-Sage.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Sage"
msgstr "Sabio saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Sage, race=black-marshes-saurians
#. [unit_type], id=Oracular Master, race=black-marshes-saurians
#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Elementalist, race=lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S2-Sage.cfg:17
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S3-Oracular_Master.cfg:85
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S2-Elementalist.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Certain saurians are seen dressed in arcane regalia and covered head to toe "
"in horrifying, esoteric shapes and markings, both with paint and tattoo. "
"Some suspect them to be visionaries, or oracles amongst their ilk. But "
"whatever ‘societal’ function they may have, they are undeniably powerful in "
"the strange magics their kind possess, and are beings to be wary of if ever "
"seen."
msgstr ""
"Ciertos saurios se ven vestidos con atuendos arcanos y cubiertos de la "
"cabeza a los pies con formas y marcas horrendas y esotéricas, tanto con "
"pintura como con tatuajes. Algunos sospechan que son visionarios u oráculos "
"entre los suyos. Pero cualquiera que sea su función «social», son "
"innegablemente poderosos en las extrañas magias que su especie posee y son "
"seres de los que hay que desconfiar si se los ve."

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=ranged
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S2-Sage.cfg:62
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S3-Oracular_Master.cfg:131
msgid "crystal flash"
msgstr "destello de cristal"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Warrior, race=black-marshes-saurians
#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Warrior, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S2-Warrior.cfg:4
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S2-Warrior(Refumee).cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Warrior"
msgstr "Guerrero saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Warrior, race=black-marshes-saurians
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S2-Warrior.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Saurian warriors are fiercely loyal to their commander and fight alongside "
"him at every opportunity."
msgstr ""
"Los guerreros saurios son ferozmente leales a su comandante y luchan a su "
"lado en cada oportunidad."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Artist, race=black-marshes-saurians
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S3-Artist.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Artist"
msgstr "Artista saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Artist, race=black-marshes-saurians
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S3-Artist.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Saurian Artist, Waklex, grew up in Dwarvish Community. His family was victim "
"of a conflict between Orcs and Dwarves in Mountains of Haag."
msgstr ""
"El artista saurio, Waklex, creció en una comunidad enana. Su familia fue "
"víctima de un conflicto entre orcos y enanos en las Montañas de Haag."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Champion, race=black-marshes-saurians
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S3-Champion.cfg:19
msgid ""
"If a saurian warrior survives enough battles he is declared a champion among "
"lizards. From a distance, he throws poisoned spears to weaken a foe before "
"he approaches, and in melee his skill with the huge spear he wields has "
"become so great that few enemies ever escape unscathed."
msgstr ""
"Si un guerrero saurio sobrevive a suficientes batallas, es declarado campeón "
"entre los lagartos. A distancia lanza lanzas envenenadas para debilitar a un "
"enemigo antes de acercarse, y en combate cuerpo a cuerpo su habilidad con la "
"enorme lanza que maneja se ha vuelto tan grande que pocos enemigos escapan "
"ilesos."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Combatant, race=black-marshes-saurians
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S3-Combatant.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Combatant"
msgstr "Combatiente saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Combatant, race=black-marshes-saurians
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S3-Combatant.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Saurian Combatant, who is one of the strongest Saurian Fighter, is an expert "
"in the use of the halberd."
msgstr ""
"El combatiente saurio, que es uno de los luchadores saurios más fuertes, es "
"un experto en el uso de la alabarda."

#. [unit_type], id=Oracular Master, race=black-marshes-saurians
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/black-marshes-saurians/S3-Oracular_Master.cfg:5
msgid "Oracular Master"
msgstr "Maestro oracular"

