#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/Hero-Zanza.cfg:4
msgid ""
"Zanza is still a young saurian of her tribe, on the verge of hatching. She "
"trained with her mother with the spear and joining her in hunts. Shortly the "
"elders recognize her great leadership potential."
msgstr ""
"Zanza todavía es una sauria joven de su tribu, a punto de salir del huevo. "
"Se entrenó con su madre usando la lanza y la acompañaba en las cacerías. "
"Pronto los ancianos reconocieron su gran potencial como líder."

#. [advancement], id=warrior_1
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/Hero-Zanza.cfg:9
msgid "<span color='#806051'><b>Warrior</b></span>\n"
msgstr "<span color='#806051'><b>Guerrera</b></span>\n"

