#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/Hero-Zanza.cfg:691
msgid "Saurian Leader"
msgstr "Líder sauria"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Devotee, race=lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S0-Devotee.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Devotee"
msgstr "Devoto saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Devotee, race=lizard, gender=male
#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Devotee Zombie, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S0-Devotee.cfg:24
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S0-Zombie-Mage.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Saurians have some knowledge of what men call sorcery, but their practice of "
"it reeks of augury and black magic. It is little understood, but rightly "
"regarded with fear by those against whom it is used."
msgstr ""
"Los saurios tienen cierto conocimiento de lo que los humanos llaman "
"hechicería, pero su práctica huele a augurios y magia negra. Es poco "
"comprendida, pero con razón se la teme por parte de aquellos contra quienes "
"se usa."

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Warrior, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S2-Warrior(Refumee).cfg:23
msgid ""
"The mainstay of the saurian army, these lizardfolk have managed to run away "
"from a proper fight enough times to understand the peril they face. "
"Bolstered by the belief in their own luck, they tend to get carved up into "
"chunks due to their reckless charges at the front line. - Grimfoot Hammerhead"
msgstr ""
"El pilar del ejército saurio. Estos lagartos han logrado escapar de una "
"pelea de verdad suficientes veces como para entender el peligro que "
"enfrentan. Animados por la creencia en su propia suerte, suelen terminar "
"hechos pedazos debido a sus cargas imprudentes en la primera línea. - "
"Grimfoot Cabezamartillo"

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=melee
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S2-Warrior(Refumee).cfg:36
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S3-Champion(Refumee).cfg:37
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S2-Pikemen.cfg:36
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S3-Heavy-Pikemen.cfg:37
msgid "halberd stab"
msgstr "estocada de alabarda"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Artificer, race=lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Artificer, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S3-Artificer(Greendragon).cfg:4
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S3-Artificer.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Artificer"
msgstr "Artífice saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Artificer, race=lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Artificer, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S3-Artificer(Greendragon).cfg:18
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S3-Artificer.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Saurians who dabble in fire magic tend to set themselves on fire due to "
"their ineptitude, which makes for a more romantic setting for the slaughter. "
"- Grimfoot Hammerhead"
msgstr ""
"Los saurios que juegan con la magia de fuego suelen prenderse fuego ellos "
"mismos debido a su ineptitud, lo que crea un escenario más romántico para la "
"masacre. - Grimfoot Cabezamartillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Champion, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S3-Champion(Refumee).cfg:24
msgid ""
"The best the lizards can offer, the so-called champions make for good boot "
"leather after careful processing. - Grimfoot Hammerhead"
msgstr ""
"Lo mejor que los lagartos pueden ofrecer. Los llamados campeones sirven para "
"hacer buen cuero de botas después de un procesamiento cuidadoso. - Grimfoot "
"Cabezamartillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Fizztsars, race=undead-lizard, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Flanker Zombie, race=undead-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S3-Fizztsars.cfg:4
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S3-Zombie-Flanker.cfg:4
msgid "female^Saurian Flanker Creeper"
msgstr "Reptadora flanqueadora sauria"

#. [unit_type], id=Fizztsars, race=undead-lizard, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Skirmisher Zombie, race=undead-lizard, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Ambusher Zombie, race=undead-lizard, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Flanker Zombie, race=undead-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S3-Fizztsars.cfg:22
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S1-Zombie-Skirmisher.cfg:18
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S2-Zombie-Ambusher.cfg:18
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S3-Zombie-Flanker.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Saurians are very small of frame, and though they are somewhat frail because "
"of this, they are very, very agile. In combat, their size allows them to "
"dart past defenses that would hold any grown man at bay, making them a "
"tricky foe to deal with.\n"
"\n"
"Spears are their preferred weapon, as their powerful hind legs can drive a "
"spear with enough force to do considerable damage, either in hand or thrown."
msgstr ""
"Los saurios son muy pequeños de complexión y, aunque son algo frágiles por "
"eso, son muy, muy ágiles. En combate, su tamaño les permite esquivar "
"defensas que detendrían a cualquier hombre adulto, lo que los convierte en "
"un enemigo difícil de manejar.\n"
"\n"
"Las lanzas son su arma preferida, ya que sus poderosas patas traseras pueden "
"impulsar una lanza con suficiente fuerza para causar un daño considerable, "
"ya sea en mano o arrojada."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S3-Fizztsars.cfg:57
msgid "plague bite"
msgstr "mordida de plaga"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Witchdoctor Alive, race=lizard, gender=male
#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Witchdoctor, race=undead-lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S3-Vendraxis-alive.cfg:4
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S3-Vendraxis.cfg:4
msgid "Vendraxis"
msgstr "Vendraxis"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Witchdoctor Alive, race=lizard, gender=male
#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Witchdoctor, race=undead-lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S3-Vendraxis-alive.cfg:24
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S3-Vendraxis.cfg:24
msgid ""
"Vendraxis is known for the campaign Secrets of the Ancients. Here he joined "
"the necromancer Ardonna. Vendraxis told her that Ardonna is not her name "
"anymore. Later an she changed her name to Ardryn-Na. He learned a lot from "
"Ardryn-Na and Ras-Tabahn. He spend years to replicate the metamorphosis and "
"was succesful. He was also succesful with convincing some of his people to "
"join his quest."
msgstr ""
"Vendraxis es conocido por la campaña Secrets of the Ancients. Aquí se unió a "
"la nigromante Ardonna. Vendraxis le dijo que Ardonna ya no era su nombre. "
"Más tarde ella cambió su nombre a Ardryn-Na. Él aprendió mucho de Ardryn-Na "
"y de Ras-Tabahn. Pasó años replicando la metamorfosis y tuvo éxito. También "
"tuvo éxito convenciendo a algunos de su pueblo para unirse a su búsqueda."

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Wise, race=lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S3-Wise.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Wise"
msgstr "Sabio saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Wise, race=lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/S3-Wise.cfg:29
msgid ""
"Saurians have some knowledge of what men call sorcery, but their practice of "
"it reeks of wisey and black magic. It is little understood, but rightly "
"regarded with fear by those against whom it is used."
msgstr ""
"Los saurios tienen cierto conocimiento de lo que los humanos llaman "
"hechicería, pero su práctica huele a adivinación y magia negra. Es poco "
"comprendida, pero con razón se la teme por parte de aquellos contra quienes "
"se usa."

#. [unit_type], id=Soulless Carrier, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/Soulless-Carrier.cfg:85
msgid "Soulless Carrier"
msgstr "Portador desalmado"

#. [unit_type], id=Soulless Carrier, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/campaign-saurians/Soulless-Carrier.cfg:100
msgid "This Soulless Saurian seems to carry something important."
msgstr "Este saurio desalmado parece llevar algo importante."

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Young Saurian, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S0-Young.cfg:23
msgid ""
"These little pests are nothing more than a prelude to the impending "
"slaughter, warming up the axe hand. - Grimfoot Hammerhead."
msgstr ""
"Estas pequeñas plagas no son más que un preludio a la masacre que se "
"avecina, calentando la mano del hacha. - Grimfoot Cabezamartillo."

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Augur, race=deep-lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S1-Augur.cfg:26
msgid ""
"Due to their annoying and constant use of magic, these augurs tend to glow "
"with an arcane aura, which just makes them a more visible target for the "
"thunder squads. - Grimfoot Hammerhead"
msgstr ""
"Debido a su molesto y constante uso de la magia, estos augures suelen "
"brillar con un aura arcana, lo que los convierte en un objetivo más visible "
"para los escuadrones de trueno. - Grimfoot Cabezamartillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Blacksmith, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S1-Blacksmith.cfg:22
msgid ""
"Saurian Blacksmiths are usually scorned by the Knalga, due to their craft "
"being at such a base level of competence. However, where one finds a "
"blacksmith, one usually finds free metals too. - Grimfoot Hammerhead"
msgstr ""
"Los herreros saurios suelen ser despreciados por los Knalga, debido a que su "
"artesanía está en un nivel tan básico de competencia. Sin embargo, donde se "
"encuentra un herrero, normalmente también se encuentran metales gratis. - "
"Grimfoot Cabezamartillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Fighter, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S1-Fighter.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Try as hard as they might, these spearmen can barely reach over our shields "
"and make a satisfying splat sound when hit with a hammer over the head. "
"-Grimfoot Hammerhead"
msgstr ""
"Por más que lo intenten, estos lanceros apenas logran pasar por encima de "
"nuestros escudos y producen un satisfactorio sonido de aplastamiento cuando "
"les golpean la cabeza con un martillo. - Grimfoot Cabezamartillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Rider, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S1-Saurianrider.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Rider"
msgstr "Jinete saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Rider, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S1-Saurianrider.cfg:23
msgid ""
"A sight to behold, barely controlling their insectoid mounts, these lizards "
"spend more time getting dragged through the dirt than actually fighting. "
"Even the most hardened dwarvish warriors tend to crack a smile at the sight. "
"- Grimfoot Hammerhead"
msgstr ""
"Un espectáculo digno de ver. Apenas controlando sus monturas insectoides, "
"estos lagartos pasan más tiempo siendo arrastrados por el suelo que luchando "
"de verdad. Incluso los guerreros enanos más endurecidos suelen sonreír al "
"verlos. - Grimfoot Cabezamartillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Armorer, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S2-Armorer.cfg:22
msgid ""
"Some saurian blacksmiths tend to live under the illusion that they are "
"better than the rest of their miserable lot, but they quickly get "
"disillusioned by a well-placed hammer blow. - Grimfoot Hammerhead"
msgstr ""
"Algunos herreros saurios tienden a vivir bajo la ilusión de que son mejores "
"que el resto de su miserable grupo, pero rápidamente se desilusionan con un "
"golpe de martillo bien colocado. - Grimfoot Cabezamartillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Craftsman, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S2-Craftsman.cfg:22
msgid ""
"These lizards are the sorriest lot of them all, stealing Knalga scraps and "
"claiming them as their own work. The feebleminded saurians tend to believe "
"such tall tales, but the dwarves just laugh at these pretenders. - Grimfoot "
"Hammerhead"
msgstr ""
"Estos lagartos son el grupo más lamentable de todos, robando restos de "
"Knalga y reclamándolos como su propio trabajo. Los saurios de mente débil "
"tienden a creer tales historias exageradas, pero los enanos solo se ríen de "
"estos impostores. - Grimfoot Cabezamartillo"

#. [attack], type=impact, range=ranged
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S2-Craftsman.cfg:58
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S3-Artisan.cfg:47
msgid "mortar"
msgstr "mortero"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Fire Ant Rider, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S2-Firerider.cfg:4
msgid "Fire Ant Rider"
msgstr "Jinete de hormiga de fuego"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Fire Ant Rider, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S2-Firerider.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Managing to survive the first months of riding a mindless beast, these "
"saurians tend to be easily dismounted by hacking a few legs from the ant. - "
"Grimfoot Hammerhead"
msgstr ""
"Logrando sobrevivir los primeros meses montando una bestia sin mente, estos "
"saurios suelen ser fácilmente desmontados cortando unas cuantas patas de la "
"hormiga. - Grimfoot Cabezamartillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Deep Saurian Peltast, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S2-Peltast.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Peltast"
msgstr "Peltasta saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Deep Saurian Peltast, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S2-Peltast.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Cowardly saurians who understand that there is no chance to fight hand-to-"
"hand against the might of the Knalga try different, albeit futile, "
"approaches to combat. They tend to believe that throwing rocks at dwarves "
"will somehow yield positive results. - Grimfoot Hammerhead"
msgstr ""
"Saurios cobardes que entienden que no tienen oportunidad de luchar cuerpo a "
"cuerpo contra el poder de Knalga intentan diferentes, aunque inútiles, "
"enfoques de combate. Tienden a creer que lanzar piedras a los enanos de "
"alguna manera dará resultados positivos. - Grimfoot Cabezamartillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Pikemen, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S2-Pikemen.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Pikeman"
msgstr "Piquero saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Pikemen, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S2-Pikemen.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Another attempt by the saurians to engage in close combat, using longer "
"spears and more experienced survivors. However, the best they can do is "
"scratch the paint on our shields. - Grimfoot Hammerhead"
msgstr ""
"Otro intento de los saurios de entrar en combate cercano, usando lanzas más "
"largas y sobrevivientes más experimentados. Sin embargo, lo mejor que pueden "
"hacer es rayar la pintura de nuestros escudos. - Grimfoot Cabezamartillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Soothsayer, race=deep-lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S2-Soothsayer.cfg:26
msgid ""
"The saurians who dabble in the healing arts are mostly weaklings who tend to "
"run at the first approach of a proper dwarvish squad. They tend to make "
"great prisoners, as other saurians will pay a handsome price for their "
"return. - Grimfoot Hammerhead"
msgstr ""
"Los saurios que se dedican a las artes de la sanación son en su mayoría "
"débiles que suelen huir al primer acercamiento de un escuadrón enano de "
"verdad. Suelen ser excelentes prisioneros, ya que otros saurios pagarán un "
"buen precio por su regreso. - Grimfoot Cabezamartillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Artisan, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S3-Artisan.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Artisan"
msgstr "Artesano saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Artisan, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S3-Artisan.cfg:23
msgid ""
"The so-called artisans of the saurians only manage to artificially prolong "
"their lifespans by standing back and throwing pebbles at the enemy. They "
"still think that rocks can damage a dwarf. It’s like trying to kill a flower "
"by watering it. - Grimfoot Hammerhead"
msgstr ""
"Los llamados artesanos de los saurios solo logran prolongar artificialmente "
"sus vidas quedándose atrás y lanzando guijarros al enemigo. Todavía creen "
"que las piedras pueden dañar a un enano. Es como intentar matar una flor "
"regándola. - Grimfoot Cabezamartillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Banner Fire Ant Rider, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S3-Banner-Firerider.cfg:4
msgid "Fire Ant Banner Rider"
msgstr "Jinete de hormiga de fuego con estandarte"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Banner Fire Ant Rider, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S3-Banner-Firerider.cfg:24
msgid ""
"The banner-carrying riders are the most eager to please saurians, even "
"carrying a piece of cloth that they can be buried in. - Grimfoot Hammerhead"
msgstr ""
"Los jinetes que portan estandartes son los saurios más ansiosos por "
"complacer, incluso llevando un trozo de tela en el que pueden ser "
"enterrados. - Grimfoot Cabezamartillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Fire Baneant Rider, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S3-Firebanerider.cfg:4
msgid "Firebane Ant Rider"
msgstr "Jinete de hormiga matafuegos"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Fire Baneant Rider, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S3-Firebanerider.cfg:24
msgid ""
"The few lucky riders who realized that making themselves a more noticeable "
"target on the battlefield train their mounts to assist them in combat. The "
"rider and the mount working in concert usually mean that the dwarf "
"encountering them has to use a backswing too. - Grimfoot Hammerhead"
msgstr ""
"Los pocos jinetes afortunados que se dieron cuenta de que hacerse un "
"objetivo más visible en el campo de batalla entrenan a sus monturas para que "
"los ayuden en combate. El jinete y la montura trabajando en conjunto suele "
"significar que el enano que los enfrenta también tiene que usar un golpe de "
"revés. - Grimfoot Cabezamartillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Deep Saurian Heavy Peltast, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S3-Heavy-Peltast.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Heavy Peltast"
msgstr "Peltasta pesado saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Deep Saurian Heavy Peltast, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S3-Heavy-Peltast.cfg:24
msgid ""
"The heavy peltast is only called heavy because of the speed at which it "
"shoots and the amount of ammo it needs. They make great wall decorations if "
"you can get your hands on one that isn’t too damaged. - Grimfoot Hammerhead"
msgstr ""
"El peltasta pesado solo se llama pesado por la velocidad a la que dispara y "
"la cantidad de munición que necesita. Son excelentes decoraciones de pared "
"si logras conseguir uno que no esté demasiado dañado. - Grimfoot "
"Cabezamartillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Heavy Pikemen, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S3-Heavy-Pikemen.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Heavy Pikeman"
msgstr "Piquero pesado saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Heavy Pikemen, race=deep-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S3-Heavy-Pikemen.cfg:24
msgid ""
"Finally wielding properly sized weapons, these saurians do tend to lead "
"charges into our ranks. Although not one has succeeded yet, they still try "
"and cling to the hope that eventually it might happen. - Grimfoot Hammerhead"
msgstr ""
"Finalmente empuñando armas del tamaño adecuado, estos saurios suelen liderar "
"cargas contra nuestras filas. Aunque ninguno ha tenido éxito todavía, siguen "
"intentándolo y se aferran a la esperanza de que algún día ocurra. - Grimfoot "
"Cabezamartillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Seer, race=deep-lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/deep-saurians/S3-Seer.cfg:27
msgid ""
"A more experienced magic user, these seers are crafty enough not to glow in "
"the dark, but still pose no real threat. Easily scared by shouting at them. "
"- Grimfoot Hammerhead"
msgstr ""
"Usuarios de magia más experimentados, estos videntes son lo suficientemente "
"astutos como para no brillar en la oscuridad, pero aún no representan una "
"amenaza real. Se asustan fácilmente si les gritas. - Grimfoot Cabezamartillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Wyrmlet, race=monster
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S0-Desert_Wyrmlet.cfg:4
msgid "Desert Wyrmlet"
msgstr "Gusano del desierto joven"

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Wyrmlet, race=monster
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S0-Desert_Wyrmlet.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Desert Wyrms are strange beasts, stout serpents with wings, but no legs. "
"They are relatively rare, and their presence is attributed to some eccentric "
"wizard or dragon. The young are small, but hungry and aggressive."
msgstr ""
"Los gusanos del desierto son bestias extrañas: serpientes robustas con alas "
"pero sin patas. Son relativamente raros y su presencia se atribuye a algún "
"mago excéntrico o dragón. Los jóvenes son pequeños, pero hambrientos y "
"agresivos."

#. [attack], type=fire, range=ranged
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S0-Desert_Wyrmlet.cfg:86
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S1-Desert_Wyrm.cfg:88
msgid "breath"
msgstr "aliento"

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Adept, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S1-Adept.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Adept"
msgstr "Adepto saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Adept, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S1-Adept.cfg:23
msgid "Only few saurians are taught in ways of the One."
msgstr "Solo unos pocos saurios son instruidos en los caminos del Uno."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=ranged
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S1-Adept.cfg:45
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S2-Priest.cfg:59
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S3-High_Priest.cfg:58
msgid "sand"
msgstr "arena"

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Wyrm, race=monster
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S1-Desert_Wyrm.cfg:5
msgid "Desert Wyrm"
msgstr "Gusano del desierto"

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Wyrm, race=monster
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S1-Desert_Wyrm.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Desert Wyrms are strange beasts, stout serpents with wings, but no legs. "
"They are relatively rare, and their presence is attributed to some eccentric "
"wizard or dragon. Mature Wyrms have excellent control of their fire breath "
"attack, as if they are themselves miniature dragons."
msgstr ""
"Los gusanos del desierto son bestias extrañas: serpientes robustas con alas "
"pero sin patas. Son relativamente raros y su presencia se atribuye a algún "
"mago excéntrico o dragón. Los gusanos maduros tienen un excelente control de "
"su ataque de aliento de fuego, como si fueran dragones en miniatura."

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Milita, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S1-Milita.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Militia"
msgstr "Milicia sauria"

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Milita, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S1-Milita.cfg:23
msgid "Young saurians take up their weapons to fight for the One."
msgstr "Los saurios jóvenes toman sus armas para luchar por el Uno."

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Slinger, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S1-Slinger.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Slinger"
msgstr "Hondero saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Slinger, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S1-Slinger.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Slingers are the skirmishers of the Golden Ones. They hunt with stones and "
"defend theirselfs with a spear."
msgstr ""
"Los honderos son los hostigadores de los Dorados. Cazan con piedras y se "
"defienden con una lanza."

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Marksman, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S2-Marksman.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Marksman"
msgstr "Tirador saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Marksman, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S2-Marksman.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Marksman are experienced slingers. They rarely missing their mark and "
"learned that stones are also useful against skeletons in the dark."
msgstr ""
"Los tiradores son honderos experimentados. Rara vez fallan su objetivo y "
"aprendieron que las piedras también son útiles contra esqueletos en la "
"oscuridad."

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Moon Priest, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S2-Moon-Priest.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Moon Priest"
msgstr "Sacerdote lunar saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Moon Priest, race=desert-lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Priest, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S2-Moon-Priest.cfg:23
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S2-Priest.cfg:23
msgid ""
"The saurians who finish their adept exam infront of a High Priest are "
"allowed enter the priesthood. They will channel the holy light to heal their "
"allies and to fight the undead."
msgstr ""
"Los saurios que terminan su examen de adepto frente a un Sumo Sacerdote "
"pueden ingresar al sacerdocio. Canalizarán la luz sagrada para sanar a sus "
"aliados y combatir a los no-muertos."

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Priest, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S2-Priest.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Priest"
msgstr "Sacerdote saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Rider Scorpion, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S2-Sand_Scuttler_Rider.cfg:4
msgid "Sand Scuttler Rider"
msgstr "Jinete de escurridor de arena"

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Rider Scorpion, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S2-Sand_Scuttler_Rider.cfg:57
msgid ""
"Only the bravest soldier can tame a Sand Scuttler and those who do this are "
"honored by their fellow saurians."
msgstr ""
"Solo el soldado más valiente puede domar a un escurridor de arena y aquellos "
"que lo logran son honrados por sus compañeros saurios."

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Soldier, race=desert-lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Soldier, race=thief-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S2-Soldier.cfg:4
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S2-Soldier.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Soldier"
msgstr "Soldado saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Soldier, race=desert-lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Squire, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S2-Soldier.cfg:23
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S2-Squire.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Militas who train a lot, gathering experience in fights or rich enough to "
"buy their equipment, are allowed to reach the rank of a soldier. They are "
"better fighters in any way."
msgstr ""
"Las milicias que entrenan mucho, acumulan experiencia en combates o son lo "
"suficientemente ricas para comprar su equipo, pueden alcanzar el rango de "
"soldado. Son mejores luchadores en todos los sentidos."

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Squire, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S2-Squire.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Squire"
msgstr "Escudero saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian High Priest, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S3-High_Priest.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian High Priest"
msgstr "Sumo sacerdote saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian High Priest, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S3-High_Priest.cfg:24
msgid ""
"Most devoted and skilled priest are allowed to meet the One and receive its "
"blessing. They will demotivate their enemies and reduces their fighting "
"strength."
msgstr ""
"Los sacerdotes más devotos y hábiles pueden reunirse con el Uno y recibir su "
"bendición. Desmoralizarán a sus enemigos y reducirán su fuerza de combate."

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Knight, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S3-Knight.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Knight"
msgstr "Caballero saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Knight, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S3-Knight.cfg:24
msgid ""
"The Knights are the elite soldiers of the Golden Ones. They lead their tribe "
"to victory. They are not like the knights of a wenothian, because the "
"saurians of the Golden one are not knowledged enough to smith armour or "
"steel swords. Besides that they should not be underestimated."
msgstr ""
"Los caballeros son los soldados de élite de los Dorados. Lideran a su tribu "
"hacia la victoria. No son como los caballeros wenothianos, porque los "
"saurios del Uno Dorado no tienen suficiente conocimiento para forjar "
"armaduras o espadas de acero. Aun así, no deben ser subestimados."

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Paladin, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S3-Paladin.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Paladin"
msgstr "Paladín saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Paladin, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S3-Paladin.cfg:24
msgid ""
"Those saurian soldiers who want to follow the teachings of the One and "
"skilled enough to be a knight, are personally handpicked by the High Priest "
"to arrange an audience with the One. Here they will receive its blessing of "
"selfheal and healing others."
msgstr ""
"Aquellos soldados saurios que desean seguir las enseñanzas del Uno y tienen "
"la habilidad suficiente para ser caballeros, son elegidos personalmente por "
"el Sumo Sacerdote para concertar una audiencia con el Uno. Allí recibirán su "
"bendición de autosanación y de sanar a otros."

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Sharpshooter, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S3-Sharpshooter.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Sharpshooter"
msgstr "Saetero saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Desert Saurian Sharpshooter, race=desert-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/desert-saurians/S3-Sharpshooter.cfg:24
msgid ""
"It seems Sharpshooters are blessed from the One, but that is wrong. The One "
"tries to teach the saurians its way, an honorable way of meele combat and "
"blessings. The Sharpshooters are the last bastion of the old culture of the "
"know called Golden Ones."
msgstr ""
"Parece que los saeteros están bendecidos por el Uno, pero eso es incorrecto. "
"El Uno intenta enseñar a los saurios su camino, una forma honorable de "
"combate cuerpo a cuerpo y bendiciones. Los tiradores de precisión son el "
"último bastión de la antigua cultura de los conocidos como los Dorados."

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Cannibal, race=lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S1-Cannibal.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Cannibal"
msgstr "Caníbal saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Cannibal, race=lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S1-Cannibal.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Saurians are known for their ability to digest nearly anything – even their "
"own kind. But the Cannibals take this to the extreme. Driven by an "
"insatiable hunger, they devour anything in their path, mending their wounds "
"with every bite."
msgstr ""
"Los saurios son conocidos por su capacidad de digerir casi cualquier cosa, "
"incluso a los de su propia especie. Pero los caníbales llevan esto al "
"extremo. Impulsados por un hambre insaciable, devoran todo lo que encuentran "
"en su camino y sanan sus heridas con cada mordisco."

#. [heal_on_hit]
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S1-Cannibal.cfg:46
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S2-Maneater.cfg:46
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S3-Liz'rker.cfg:47
msgid "omnivore"
msgstr "omnívoro"

#. [heal_on_hit]
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S1-Cannibal.cfg:47
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S1-Cannibal.cfg:48
msgid "This unit heals itself for 1 hitpoint when it deals damage."
msgstr "Esta unidad se sana 1 punto de vida cuando causa daño."

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Dragonfly Rider, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S1-Dragonfly_Rider.cfg:5
msgid "Dragonfly Rider"
msgstr "Jinete de libélula"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Dragonfly Rider, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S1-Dragonfly_Rider.cfg:27
msgid ""
"The giant dragonflies seen in some of the swamps, rivers, and lakes around "
"Wesnoth enjoy a longer life cycle than the smaller, more common types. The "
"adult form can live indefinitely, slowly growing to a final moult. They are "
"generally territorial, but can cooperate in small groups to confront common "
"foes or large prey. Some saurians tend to tame them as mounts."
msgstr ""
"Las libélulas gigantes que se ven en algunos pantanos, ríos y lagos "
"alrededor de Wesnoth tienen un ciclo de vida más largo que las variedades "
"más pequeñas y comunes. La forma adulta puede vivir indefinidamente, "
"creciendo lentamente hasta su muda final. Generalmente son territoriales, "
"pero pueden cooperar en pequeños grupos para enfrentar enemigos comunes o "
"presas grandes. Algunos saurios suelen domesticarlas como monturas."

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Shaman, race=lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S1-Shaman.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Shaman"
msgstr "Chamán saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Shaman, race=lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S1-Shaman.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Saurians have some knowledge of what men call sorcery, but their practice of "
"it reeks of augury and black magic. Shamans however practice element magic "
"like fire and ice."
msgstr ""
"Los saurios tienen cierto conocimiento de lo que los humanos llaman "
"hechicería, pero su práctica huele a augurios y magia negra. Los chamanes, "
"sin embargo, practican magia elemental como fuego y hielo."

#. [special_note]
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S1-Shaman.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Saurian Shamans' innate magical abilities shield them against arcane, fire, "
"and cold damage."
msgstr ""
"Las habilidades mágicas innatas de los chamanes saurios los protegen contra "
"daño arcano, de fuego y de frío."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Scout, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S1_Scout.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Scout"
msgstr "Explorador saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Scout, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S1_Scout.cfg:24
msgid ""
"Saurian Scouts are swift and nimble, excelling at exploring unknown terrain "
"and identifying potential dangers or opportunities. Their keen senses and "
"agility allow them to evade enemies with ease, making them invaluable for "
"reconnaissance missions. Armed with simple tools and their natural cunning, "
"they can move through areas that most others would consider impassable."
msgstr ""
"Los exploradores saurios son rápidos y ágiles, destacan en explorar terrenos "
"desconocidos e identificar posibles peligros u oportunidades. Sus sentidos "
"agudos y su agilidad les permiten evadir enemigos con facilidad, lo que los "
"hace muy valiosos para misiones de reconocimiento. Armados con herramientas "
"simples y su astucia natural, pueden moverse por áreas que la mayoría "
"consideraría intransitables."

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Grand Dragonfly Raider, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S2-Dragonfly_Raider.cfg:5
msgid "Grand Dragonfly Raider"
msgstr "Asaltante de gran libélula"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Grand Dragonfly Raider, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S2-Dragonfly_Raider.cfg:27
msgid ""
"Some saurian dragonfly rider bond long enough with their dragonfly to see "
"their grander form."
msgstr ""
"Algunos jinetes saurios de libélula se vinculan el tiempo suficiente con su "
"libélula como para ver su forma más grandiosa."

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Maneater, race=lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S2-Maneater.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Maneater"
msgstr "Devorador saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Maneater, race=lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S2-Maneater.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Having feasted on countless foes, the Maneater has grown into a relentless "
"predator. With each strike, it tears into its enemies, sustaining itself by "
"feeding on the flesh of the fallen."
msgstr ""
"Después de haberse alimentado de innumerables enemigos, el devorador se ha "
"convertido en un depredador implacable. Con cada golpe desgarra a sus "
"enemigos y se sustenta alimentándose de la carne de los caídos."

#. [heal_on_hit]
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S2-Maneater.cfg:47
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S2-Maneater.cfg:48
msgid "This unit heals itself for 2 hitpoint when it deals damage."
msgstr "Esta unidad se sana 2 puntos de vida cuando causa daño."

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Mireblade, race=thief-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S2-Mireblade.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Mireblade"
msgstr "Hoja de pantano saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Mireblade, race=thief-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S2-Mireblade.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Saurian Mireblades refine the agility and stealth of their scouting origins "
"into a deadly combat style. Experts at nocturnal ambushes, they strike "
"swiftly and silently, leaving their foes disoriented and vulnerable. Their "
"blades are often coated with poison, turning even minor wounds into "
"debilitating threats. To further confound their enemies, they use smoke "
"bombs to obscure their movements, making it nearly impossible to pin them "
"down. Mireblades are shadowy figures of the battlefield, thriving in chaos "
"and confusion."
msgstr ""
"Las hojas de pantano saurias refinan la agilidad y el sigilo de sus orígenes "
"como exploradores en un estilo de combate mortal. Expertos en emboscadas "
"nocturnas, atacan con rapidez y en silencio, dejando a sus enemigos "
"desorientados y vulnerables. Sus hojas suelen estar cubiertas de veneno, "
"convirtiendo incluso heridas menores en amenazas debilitantes. Para "
"confundir aún más a sus enemigos, usan bombas de humo para ocultar sus "
"movimientos, haciendo casi imposible fijarlos. Las hojas de pantano son "
"figuras sombrías en el campo de batalla que prosperan en el caos y la "
"confusión."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Pathfinder, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S2_Pathfinder.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Pathfinder"
msgstr "Buscador de caminos saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Pathfinder, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S2_Pathfinder.cfg:24
msgid ""
"As Saurian Scouts gain experience, they evolve into adept pathfinders. These "
"warriors combine their natural mobility with sharper instincts and better "
"equipment, enabling them to navigate even the most challenging terrain with "
"precision. Whether uncovering hidden threats or tracking prey, Saurian "
"Pathfinders play a pivotal role in ensuring their kin's survival. Their "
"ability to strike swiftly and retreat unscathed makes them a thorn in the "
"side of unprepared foes."
msgstr ""
"A medida que los exploradores saurios ganan experiencia, evolucionan hacia "
"buscadores de caminos hábiles. Estos guerreros combinan su movilidad natural "
"con instintos más agudos y mejor equipo, lo que les permite navegar con "
"precisión incluso por los terrenos más difíciles. Ya sea descubriendo "
"amenazas ocultas o rastreando presas, los buscadores de caminos saurios "
"juegan un papel clave para garantizar la supervivencia de los suyos. Su "
"capacidad para atacar con rapidez y retirarse ilesos los convierte en una "
"espina clavada para los enemigos desprevenidos."

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Grand Dragonfly Chief, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S3-Dragonfly_Chief.cfg:5
msgid "Grand Dragonfly Chief"
msgstr "Jefe de gran libélula"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Grand Dragonfly Chief, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S3-Dragonfly_Chief.cfg:28
msgid ""
"Saurians who master the grander dragonfly form, are masters of the skys."
msgstr ""
"Los saurios que dominan la forma más grandiosa de la libélula son maestros "
"de los cielos."

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Lizrker, race=lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S3-Liz'rker.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Liz'rker"
msgstr "Devorador saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Lizrker, race=lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S3-Liz'rker.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Now a true embodiment of hunger and fury, the Liz'rker is an unstoppable "
"force of destruction. Tearing through flesh and bone, it fights in a frenzy, "
"using every kill to fuel its relentless assault."
msgstr ""
"Ahora una verdadera encarnación del hambre y la furia, el devorador saurio "
"es una fuerza imparable de destrucción. Desgarrando carne y hueso, lucha en "
"un frenesí, usando cada muerte para alimentar su asalto implacable."

#. [heal_on_hit]
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S3-Liz'rker.cfg:48
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S3-Liz'rker.cfg:49
msgid "This unit heals itself for 3 hitpoint when it deals damage."
msgstr "Esta unidad se sana 3 puntos de vida cuando causa daño."

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Master of Elements, race=lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S3-Master_of_Elements.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Master of Elements"
msgstr "Maestro de los elementos saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Master of Elements, race=lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S3-Master_of_Elements.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Master of elements mastered the fire and ice magic of their tribe. Their are "
"no masters in a human kind of sense, but very skillfull."
msgstr ""
"El maestro de los elementos domina la magia de fuego y hielo de su tribu. No "
"son maestros en el sentido humano, pero son muy hábiles."

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Stillwater, race=thief-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S3-Stillwater.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Stillwater"
msgstr "Aguas quietas saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Stillwater, race=thief-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S3-Stillwater.cfg:18
msgid ""
"The evolution of a Mireblade, Saurian Stillwaters are the epitome of silent "
"lethality. Masters of deception and ambush, they move like shadows, striking "
"with poisoned weapons and vanishing before the enemy can react. Their "
"expertise with smoke bombs allows them to control the battlefield, creating "
"a veil of confusion that leaves their opponents defenseless. Unpredictable "
"and unrelenting, Stillwaters embody the deadly calm of a predator lying in "
"wait, striking fear into those who dare oppose them."
msgstr ""
"La evolución de una hoja de pantano, los aguas quietas saurios son el "
"epítome de la letalidad silenciosa. Maestros del engaño y la emboscada, se "
"mueven como sombras, atacando con armas envenenadas y desapareciendo antes "
"de que el enemigo pueda reaccionar. Su pericia con las bombas de humo les "
"permite controlar el campo de batalla, creando un velo de confusión que deja "
"a sus oponentes indefensos. Impredecibles e implacables, los aguas quietas "
"encarnan la calma mortal de un depredador al acecho, infundiendo miedo en "
"aquellos que se atreven a oponérseles."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Explorer, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S3_Explorer.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Explorer"
msgstr "Explorador saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Explorer, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/saurians/S3_Explorer.cfg:25
msgid ""
"The Saurian Explorer embodies the culmination of their species’ adaptability "
"and curiosity. These seasoned scouts are unparalleled in charting unknown "
"lands and uncovering hidden opportunities. With their unmatched agility and "
"deep knowledge of the terrain, they are capable of venturing into the most "
"treacherous regions and returning unscathed.\n"
"\n"
"Whether mapping uncharted paths, locating hidden resources, or identifying "
"potential threats, the Saurian Explorer ensures their kin are always one "
"step ahead. Their ability to outmaneuver foes and operate independently "
"makes them a true asset in both strategy and survival."
msgstr ""
"El explorador saurio encarna la culminación de la adaptabilidad y curiosidad "
"de su especie. Estos exploradores experimentados no tienen igual para trazar "
"tierras desconocidas y descubrir oportunidades ocultas. Con su agilidad "
"inigualable y su profundo conocimiento del terreno, son capaces de "
"aventurarse en las regiones más traicioneras y regresar ilesos.\n"
"\n"
"Ya sea trazando caminos inexplorados, localizando recursos ocultos o "
"identificando amenazas potenciales, el explorador saurio asegura que los "
"suyos siempre estén un paso adelante. Su capacidad para superar a los "
"enemigos y operar de forma independiente los convierte en un verdadero "
"activo tanto en estrategia como en supervivencia."

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Brawler Thief, race=thief-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S1-Brawler-thief.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Brawler Thief"
msgstr "Luchador ladrón saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Brawler Thief, race=thief-lizard, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Brawler, race=thief-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S1-Brawler-thief.cfg:18
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S1-Brawler.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Saurian tribes rarely maintain anything resembling a standing army, fighting "
"primarily with hit-and-run raiding tactics by the tribe's hunters and "
"scouts. The largest and strongest saurians are often designated to defend "
"the village and serve as shock troops in time of war. Being the closest "
"thing the tribe has to dedicated soldiers, they generally prefer the club "
"over the traditional saurian hunting spear, making them all the more "
"effective in battles against rival tribes."
msgstr ""
"Las tribus saurias rara vez mantienen algo parecido a un ejército permanente "
"y luchan principalmente con tácticas de ataque rápido y huida por parte de "
"los cazadores y exploradores de la tribu. Los saurios más grandes y fuertes "
"suelen ser designados para defender la aldea y servir como tropas de choque "
"en tiempos de guerra. Al ser lo más cercano que tiene la tribu a soldados "
"dedicados, generalmente prefieren la porra sobre la lanza de caza "
"tradicional sauria, lo que los hace aún más efectivos en batallas contra "
"tribus rivales."

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Brawler, race=thief-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S1-Brawler.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Brawler"
msgstr "Luchador saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Hunter Thief, race=thief-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S1-Hunter-thief.cfg:5
msgid "Saurian Hunter Thief"
msgstr "Cazador ladrón saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Hunter Thief, race=thief-lizard, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Hunter, race=lizard, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Lurker Thief, race=thief-lizard, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Lurker, race=lizard, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Stalker Thief, race=thief-lizard, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Stalker, race=lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S1-Hunter-thief.cfg:30
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S1-Hunter.cfg:30
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S2-Lurker-thief.cfg:30
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S2-Lurker.cfg:30
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S3-Stalker-thief.cfg:31
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S3-Stalker.cfg:31
msgid ""
"While saurians are known for their speed, their cold blodded nature allows "
"them to hold their breath for long periods of time. With practice, a saurian "
"can remain underwater, lurking just below the surface to ambush those who "
"come too near the water's edge."
msgstr ""
"Aunque los saurios son conocidos por su velocidad, su naturaleza de sangre "
"fría les permite contener la respiración durante largos periodos. Con "
"práctica, un saurio puede permanecer bajo el agua, acechando justo debajo de "
"la superficie para emboscar a aquellos que se acercan demasiado al borde del "
"agua."

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Knifethrower Thief, race=thief-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S1-Knifethrower-thief.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Knifethrower Thief"
msgstr "Lanzacuchillos ladrón saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Knifethrower, race=thief-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S1-Knifethrower.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Knifethrower"
msgstr "Lanzacuchillos saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Lurker Thief, race=thief-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S2-Lurker-thief.cfg:5
msgid "Saurian Lurker Thief"
msgstr "Acechador ladrón saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Lurker, race=lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S2-Lurker.cfg:5
msgid "Saurian Lurker"
msgstr "Acechador saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Seeker Thief, race=thief-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S2-Seeker-thief.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Seeker Thief"
msgstr "Buscador ladrón saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Seeker Thief, race=thief-lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Seeker, race=thief-lizard
#. [unit_type], id=GSaurian Ambusher, race=undead-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S2-Seeker-thief.cfg:17
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S2-Seeker.cfg:17
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S2-Ghost-Ambusher.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Saurians are light on their feet, and able at navigating terrain that often "
"confounds their enemies. When this natural mobility is combined with "
"experience, strength, and proper equipment, their warriors can become "
"particularly threatening in battle — if only because they are so much more "
"difficult to confine than other foes. Even in armor, saurian warriors can "
"take advantage of the smallest gap in an enemy line, and have the prowess to "
"make the enemy regret tactical mistakes."
msgstr ""
"Los saurios son ligeros de pies y capaces de navegar por terrenos que suelen "
"confundir a sus enemigos. Cuando esta movilidad natural se combina con "
"experiencia, fuerza y equipo adecuado, sus guerreros pueden volverse "
"particularmente amenazantes en batalla, aunque solo sea porque son mucho más "
"difíciles de contener que otros enemigos. Incluso con armadura, los "
"guerreros saurios pueden aprovechar el más pequeño hueco en la línea enemiga "
"y tienen la destreza para hacer que el enemigo se arrepienta de sus errores "
"tácticos."

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Seeker, race=thief-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S2-Seeker.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Seeker"
msgstr "Buscador saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Soldier Thief, race=thief-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S2-Soldier-thief.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Soldier Thief"
msgstr "Soldado ladrón saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Soldier Thief, race=thief-lizard, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Soldier, race=thief-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S2-Soldier-thief.cfg:18
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S2-Soldier.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Saurian Brawlers are experts in the use of the club. They are fiercely loyal "
"to their tribe and fight alongside their champions at every opportunity."
msgstr ""
"Los luchadores saurios son expertos en el uso de la porra. Son ferozmente "
"leales a su tribu y luchan junto a sus campeones en cada oportunidad."

#. [unit_type], id=Swamp Rider Thief, race=thief-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S2-Swamp-rider-thief.cfg:13
msgid "Swamp Rider Thief"
msgstr "Jinete del pantano ladrón"

#. [unit_type], id=Swamp Rider Thief, race=thief-lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Swamp Rider, race=lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Great Swamp Rider Thief, race=thief-lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Great Swamp Rider, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S2-Swamp-rider-thief.cfg:121
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S2-Swamp-rider.cfg:121
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S3-Great-Swamp-rider-thief.cfg:122
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S3-Great-Swamp-rider.cfg:122
msgid ""
"Swamps are vibrant environments, but often not friendly to humans or orcs. "
"Swamp Lizards are one of the more notable hazards, with their powerful jaws "
"and armored hide. Despite their primitive appearance, these lizards are not "
"stupid, and after generations of being hunted for their hides, they have "
"adopted a ‘two legs bad’ outlook and do not hesitate to avenge their "
"ancestors."
msgstr ""
"Los pantanos son entornos vibrantes, pero a menudo no son amigables para "
"humanos u orcos. Los lagartos de pantano son uno de los peligros más "
"notables, con sus poderosas mandíbulas y su piel blindada. A pesar de su "
"apariencia primitiva, estos lagartos no son tontos y, después de "
"generaciones de ser cazados por sus pieles, han adoptado la visión de que "
"«dos piernas son malas» y no dudan en vengar a sus ancestros."

#. [unit_type], id=Swamp Rider, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S2-Swamp-rider.cfg:13
msgid "Swamp Rider"
msgstr "Jinete del pantano"

#. [unit_type], id=Great Swamp Rider Thief, race=thief-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S3-Great-Swamp-rider-thief.cfg:13
msgid "Great Swamp Rider Thief"
msgstr "Gran jinete de pantano ladrón"

#. [unit_type], id=Great Swamp Rider, race=lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S3-Great-Swamp-rider.cfg:13
msgid "Great Swamp Rider"
msgstr "Gran jinete de pantano"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Slayer Thief, race=thief-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S3-Slayer-thief.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Slayer Thief"
msgstr "Asesino ladrón saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Slayer Thief, race=thief-lizard
#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Slayer, race=thief-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S3-Slayer-thief.cfg:18
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S3-Slayer.cfg:18
msgid ""
"The saurian slayer coats the dagger in poison, and has mastered the act of "
"throwing knives at the distance."
msgstr ""
"El asesino saurio cubre la daga con veneno y ha dominado el arte de lanzar "
"cuchillos a distancia."

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Slayer, race=thief-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S3-Slayer.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Slayer"
msgstr "Asesino saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Stalker Thief, race=thief-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S3-Stalker-thief.cfg:5
msgid "Saurian Stalker Thief"
msgstr "Acechador ladrón saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Stalker, race=lizard, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Undead Stalker, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S3-Stalker.cfg:5
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S3-Stalker.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Stalker"
msgstr "Acechador saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Veteran Thief, race=thief-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S3-Veteran-thief.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Veteran Thief"
msgstr "Veterano ladrón saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Veteran Thief, race=thief-lizard, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Veteran, race=thief-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S3-Veteran-thief.cfg:19
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S3-Veteran.cfg:19
msgid ""
"The strongest of their tribe, each combatant is an seasoned veteran who has "
"enjoyed shattering the bones of countless opponents and cracking their "
"skulls as an offering after the battles."
msgstr ""
"Los más fuertes de su tribu, cada combatiente es un veterano experimentado "
"que ha disfrutado rompiendo los huesos de innumerables oponentes y "
"abriéndoles el cráneo como ofrenda después de las batallas."

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Veteran, race=thief-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/thief-saurians/S3-Veteran.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Veteran"
msgstr "Veterano saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Saurian Devotee Zombie, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S0-Zombie-Mage.cfg:4
msgid "Mage Walking Corpse"
msgstr "Cadáver andante mago"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Young Saurian Zombie, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S0-Zombie-Pick.cfg:4
msgid "Pick Walking Corpse"
msgstr "Cadáver andante con pico"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Young Saurian Zombie, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S0-Zombie-Pick.cfg:18
msgid "Young Saurians work mostly as miners."
msgstr "Los saurios jóvenes trabajan principalmente como mineros."

#. [unit_type], id=Ref Young Saurian Zombie, race=undead-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S0-Zombie-Spear.cfg:4
msgid "Spear Walking Corpse"
msgstr "Cadáver andante con lanza"

#. [unit_type], id=Lich Saurian Augur, race=undead-lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S1-Augur-Lich.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Dark Augur"
msgstr "Augur oscuro saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Lich Saurian Augur, race=undead-lizard, gender=male
#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Dark Adept, race=undead-lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S1-Augur-Lich.cfg:22
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S1-Saurian-Dark-Adept.cfg:22
msgid ""
"These saurians follow Vendraxis and his teachings of the ways of necromancy."
msgstr ""
"Estos saurios siguen a Vendraxis y sus enseñanzas sobre los caminos de la "
"nigromancia."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Ghoul, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S1-Ghoul.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Ghoul"
msgstr "Ghoul saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Ghoul, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S1-Ghoul.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Vendraxis’ first attempt at creating a ghoul went terribly wrong. Following "
"the methods taught by Ardryn-Na, he failed to anticipate the unique bone "
"structure of saurians, which caused the flesh to decay and refuse to bond "
"properly. What remained was a poisonous, lumbering mass of saurian flesh — a "
"failed experiment, but a dangerous one nonetheless."
msgstr ""
"El primer intento de Vendraxis de crear un ghoul salió terriblemente mal. "
"Siguiendo los métodos enseñados por Ardryn-Na, no anticipó la estructura "
"ósea única de los saurios, lo que hizo que la carne se pudriera y se negara "
"a unirse correctamente. Lo que quedó fue una masa venenosa y torpe de carne "
"sauria: un experimento fallido, pero peligroso de todos modos."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Dark Adept, race=undead-lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S1-Saurian-Dark-Adept.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Dark Adept"
msgstr "Adepto oscuro saurio"

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=ranged
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S1-Saurian-Dark-Adept.cfg:41
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S2-Saurian-Dark-Sorcerer.cfg:53
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S3-Saurian-Necromancer.cfg:64
msgid "shadow blast"
msgstr "explosión de sombras"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Husk, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S1-Saurian_Husk.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Husk"
msgstr "Cáscara sauria"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Husk, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S1-Saurian_Husk.cfg:24
msgid ""
"The practice of necromancy is unknown among the saurians, but their augurs "
"practice other arts, older and equally vile. The most terrible of these uses "
"an elixir of rare herbs and dark rituals to induce a deathlike trance in "
"their still-living brethren; in this state the lifeless husks act as barely-"
"sentient slaves, commanded by their creators' dark magics. It is speculated "
"by some loremasters that these creatures are a precursor to the vile ghoul, "
"and that human necromancers learned such craft from the saurians. Few have a "
"chance to study these unliving abominations in detail, however; while alone "
"these shambling forms may seem slow and clumsy, they retain a deadly pack "
"instinct and once they have their prey surrounded they rip into it with "
"astonishing speed and viciousness."
msgstr ""
"La práctica de la nigromancia es desconocida entre los saurios, pero sus "
"augures practican otras artes más antiguas e igualmente viles. La más "
"terrible de estas usa un elixir de hierbas raras y rituales oscuros para "
"inducir un trance similar a la muerte en sus hermanos aún vivos; en este "
"estado las cáscaras sin vida actúan como esclavos apenas conscientes, "
"comandados por las magias oscuras de sus creadores. Algunos sabios especulan "
"que estas criaturas son un precursor del vil ghoul y que los nigromantes "
"humanos aprendieron tal arte de los saurios. Sin embargo, pocos tienen la "
"oportunidad de estudiar estas abominaciones no vivas en detalle; aunque "
"solas estas formas tambaleantes pueden parecer lentas y torpes, conservan un "
"instinto de manada mortal y una vez que rodean a su presa la desgarran con "
"una velocidad y ferocidad asombrosas."

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Blacksmith Zombie, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S1-Zombie-Blacksmith.cfg:4
msgid "Soulless Saurian Blacksmith"
msgstr "Herrero saurio desalmado"

#. [unit_type], id=Deep Saurian Blacksmith Zombie, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S1-Zombie-Blacksmith.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Some lizards prefer to keep working for the community, instead of becoming "
"warriors. The novice blacksmith is one of such, their crude craft helps the "
"tribe as they create new armor and weapons."
msgstr ""
"Algunos lagartos prefieren seguir trabajando para la comunidad en lugar de "
"convertirse en guerreros. El herrero novato es uno de ellos; su artesanía "
"rudimentaria ayuda a la tribu al crear nuevas armaduras y armas."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Skirmisher Zombie, race=undead-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S1-Zombie-Skirmisher.cfg:4
msgid "female^Soulless Saurian Skirmisher"
msgstr "Hostigadora sauria desalmada"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Flayer, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S2-Flayer.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Flayer"
msgstr "Desollador saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Flayer, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S2-Flayer.cfg:18
msgid ""
"An odd twist of fate turned the Saurian Flayer into what it is today. "
"Vendraxis accidentally left several Ghouls abandoned in a toxic swamp. Over "
"time, they adapted, learning to hide and to transform their saliva into a "
"burning, poisonous acid. Why this mutation occurred remains a mystery, but "
"it has become one of Vendraxis' most dangerous successes."
msgstr ""
"Un giro extraño del destino convirtió al desollador saurio en lo que es hoy. "
"Vendraxis dejó accidentalmente varios guls abandonados en un pantano tóxico. "
"Con el tiempo se adaptaron, aprendiendo a esconderse y a transformar su "
"saliva en un ácido ardiente y venenoso. Por qué ocurrió esta mutación sigue "
"siendo un misterio, pero se ha convertido en uno de los éxitos más "
"peligrosos de Vendraxis."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Runner, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S2-Runner.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Runner"
msgstr "Corredor saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Runner, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S2-Runner.cfg:18
msgid ""
"The Saurian Runner is what happens when a Saurian Ghoul undergoes intense "
"muscle training. It has developed incredible speed, but at the cost of "
"control. These creatures charge into battle at blinding velocity, often "
"unable to stop before slamming into their targets, making them both "
"unpredictable and deadly."
msgstr ""
"El corredor saurio es lo que ocurre cuando un ghoul saurio se somete a un "
"intenso entrenamiento muscular. Ha desarrollado una velocidad increíble, "
"pero a costa del control. Estas criaturas cargan en batalla a una velocidad "
"cegadora, a menudo sin poder detenerse antes de estrellarse contra sus "
"objetivos, lo que las hace impredecibles y mortales."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Dark Sorcerer, race=undead-lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S2-Saurian-Dark-Sorcerer.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Dark Sorcerer"
msgstr "Hechicero oscuro saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Dark Sorcerer, race=undead-lizard, gender=male
#. [unit_type], id=Lich Saurian Soothsayer, race=undead-lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S2-Saurian-Dark-Sorcerer.cfg:22
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S2-Soothsayer-Lich.cfg:22
msgid ""
"Saurian Sorcerer are skilled Adepts of Vendraxis. They learned to force "
"their will on the dead."
msgstr ""
"Los hechiceros saurios son adeptos hábiles de Vendraxis. Aprendieron a "
"imponer su voluntad sobre los muertos."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Wretch, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S2-Saurian_Wretch.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Wretch"
msgstr "Miserable saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Wretch, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S2-Saurian_Wretch.cfg:24
msgid ""
"Some Saurian Husks begin to show a disturbing evolution. As their bodies "
"adapt to the unnatural magic animating them, they grow more agile and "
"ruthless. No longer mere lifeless puppets, they develop a predatory cunning "
"and a savage instinct to hunt their prey. These wretches, though grotesque "
"and broken, are a terrifying step towards a darker, more destructive form."
msgstr ""
"Algunas cáscaras saurias comienzan a mostrar una evolución inquietante. A "
"medida que sus cuerpos se adaptan a la magia antinatural que los anima, se "
"vuelven más ágiles y despiadados. Ya no son simples marionetas sin vida, "
"desarrollan una astucia depredadora y un instinto salvaje para cazar a su "
"presa. Estos miserables, aunque grotescos y rotos, son un paso aterrador "
"hacia una forma más oscura y destructiva."

#. [unit_type], id=Lich Saurian Soothsayer, race=undead-lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S2-Soothsayer-Lich.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Dark Soothsayer"
msgstr "Adivino oscuro saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Ambusher Zombie, race=undead-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S2-Zombie-Ambusher.cfg:4
msgid "female^Saurian Ambusher Zombie"
msgstr "Emboscadora zombi sauria"

#. [unit_type], id=GSaurian Flanker, race=undead-lizard, gender=female
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S3-Ghost-Flanker.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Saurian warriors are generally weaker in frame than their elven or human "
"counterparts. This is of course a relative term, and they can still become "
"considerably powerful, whilst losing none of their natural mobility. This is "
"very dangerous in combat, as a careless enemy can soon find their support "
"troops flanked by these creatures."
msgstr ""
"Los guerreros saurios generalmente tienen un cuerpo más débil que sus "
"contrapartes elfas o humanas. Esto es, por supuesto, un término relativo, y "
"aún pueden volverse considerablemente poderosos sin perder su movilidad "
"natural. Esto es muy peligroso en combate, ya que un enemigo descuidado "
"pronto puede encontrarse con que sus tropas de apoyo están flanqueadas por "
"estas criaturas."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Necromancer, race=undead-lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S3-Saurian-Necromancer.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Necromancer"
msgstr "Nigromante saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Necromancer, race=undead-lizard, gender=male
#. [unit_type], id=Lich Saurian Seer, race=undead-lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S3-Saurian-Necromancer.cfg:23
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S3-Seer-Lich.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Saurian Necromancers are close to Vendraxis power. They are able to lead "
"whole armies of undead against their foes."
msgstr ""
"Los nigromantes saurios están cerca del poder de Vendraxis. Son capaces de "
"liderar ejércitos enteros de no-muertos contra sus enemigos."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Blight, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S3-Saurian_Blight.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Blight"
msgstr "Plaga sauria"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Blight, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S3-Saurian_Blight.cfg:25
msgid ""
"The final and most horrifying form of a Saurian Wretch is the Saurian "
"Blight. What was once a living being is now a walking embodiment of decay "
"and death. Its rotting form emits a foul aura, poisoning and corrupting "
"everything in its path. With immense strength and an insatiable hunger for "
"destruction, these abominations are the ultimate expression of their "
"creators' dark rituals, leaving only devastation in their wake."
msgstr ""
"La forma final y más horrible de un miserable saurio es la plaga sauria. Lo "
"que alguna vez fue un ser vivo ahora es una encarnación andante de la "
"decadencia y la muerte. Su forma putrefacta emite un aura repugnante que "
"envenena y corrompe todo a su paso. Con una fuerza inmensa y un hambre "
"insaciable de destrucción, estas abominaciones son la expresión definitiva "
"de los rituales oscuros de sus creadores, dejando solo devastación a su paso."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=melee
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S3-Saurian_Blight.cfg:48
msgid "charging bite"
msgstr "mordida en carga"

#. [unit_type], id=Lich Saurian Seer, race=undead-lizard, gender=male
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S3-Seer-Lich.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Dark Seer"
msgstr "Vidente oscuro saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Sprinter, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S3-Sprinter.cfg:4
msgid "Saurian Sprinter"
msgstr "Velocista saurio"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Sprinter, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S3-Sprinter.cfg:19
msgid ""
"The Saurian Sprinter is the perfected form of the Runner. After mastering "
"its overwhelming speed, it now strikes with precision, controlling its every "
"movement. These creatures are not just fast—they are terrifyingly accurate, "
"capable of delivering swift, lethal blows to their enemies with surgical "
"precision."
msgstr ""
"El velocista saurio es la forma perfeccionada del corredor. Después de "
"dominar su abrumadora velocidad, ahora ataca con precisión y controla cada "
"movimiento. Estas criaturas no solo son rápidas, son terriblemente precisas, "
"capaces de asestar golpes rápidos y letales a sus enemigos con precisión "
"quirúrgica."

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Undead Stalker, race=undead-lizard
#: Refumees_Saurian_Pack/units/undead-saurians/S3-Stalker.cfg:19
msgid ""
"The Saurian Stalker is the ultimate evolution of the Flayer, trained under "
"the guidance of a master. These creatures have perfected the art of spitting "
"corrosive acid and can now conceal themselves in various terrains—whether in "
"the depths of a swamp, beneath the sands of a desert, or in the shadows of a "
"dark cave. They strike with deadly precision, emerging from hiding to "
"surprise their enemies."
msgstr ""
"El acechador saurio es la evolución definitiva del desollador, entrenado "
"bajo la guía de un maestro. Estas criaturas han perfeccionado el arte de "
"escupir ácido corrosivo y ahora pueden ocultarse en diversos terrenos, ya "
"sea en las profundidades de un pantano, bajo las arenas de un desierto o en "
"las sombras de una cueva oscura. Atacan con una precisión mortal, emergiendo "
"de su escondite para sorprender a sus enemigos."
